0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26510:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Australian web hosting? When building a website, it’s important to choose the best web hosting service in order to get the speed, performance, security, and support you need. Choosing the wrong web host can make your website unreliable, which can negatively impact your website traffic, SEO, and even conversions. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share with you our picks for the 10 best Australian web hosting services. Not all of the web hosting providers on this list are based in Australia, but all of them are able to deliver the quality service you’re looking for. </p>\n<p>Let’s get started. </p>\n<h2>Web Hosting Australia Review: Our Process</h2>\n<p>Before we get into our top 10 picks for the best web hosting Australia, we want to share our IsItWP web hosting review process. </p>\n<p>We’ve tested many of the web hosts on this list ourselves so that we can provide you with a detailed review. We hope that this will make the process of choosing the best Australian web hosting service easier for you. There’s no need to waste your time trying out a bunch of different Australian web hosts since we’ve done it for you. </p>\n<p>We tested these web hosts by performing the following steps: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>Signed up with the best Australian web hosting services. </li>\n<li>Built a test WordPress website.</li>\n<li>Added a WordPress theme, images and dummy content to mirror a live site environment. </li>\n<li>Performed speed tests to see how the site would work and recorded the test data.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>As you can see, we put these web hosts to the test, which is why we’re confident in this list of the best Australian web hosting services. </p>\n<p>Let’s get started!</p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >1. SiteGround</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-canada-1.jpg\" alt=\"siteground-australia\" width=\"370\" height=\"195\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-235334\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-canada-1.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-canada-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 649 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 10/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SiteGround.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with SiteGround &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >SiteGround</a> is one of the best Australian web hosting services and they’re the trusted web host of over 2 million domains. </p>\n<p>Building your website is easy with SiteGround. You can choose from free WordPress installation (the most popular content management system in the world) or the Weebly site builder. Both options allow you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">make a website</a> in no time. </p>\n<p>SiteGround provides top-notch customer support that’s available by 24/7 via phone, live chat, and tickets. So, no matter the issue you have, you can count on quick, reliable pickup and resolution. </p>\n<p>Plus, SiteGround offers some of the fastest web hosting on the market. They have a data center located in Singapore, which work