ts you highlight your most important content on the homepage with a plain white layout, image slider, and audio player. Promenade offers 30+ handpicked to give a unique appearance to your site.</p>\n<p>It has a section to share your featured videos, songs, and upcoming events. Promenade supports tons of social networks so you can connect with your users.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/audiotheme-marquee/\" title=\"Marquee\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">16. Marquee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/audiotheme-marquee/\" title=\"Marquee\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/marquee.jpg\" alt=\"Marquee\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233979\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/marquee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/marquee-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/marquee-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/audiotheme-marquee/\" title=\"Marquee\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Marquee</a> is a minimal WordPress music theme. It has a split screen layout with prominent branding on the left and content on the right for desktop-sized screens. </p>\n<p>This theme offers custom fonts, color choices, backgrounds, and more. The theme also lets you showcase your upcoming gigs, so your fans know where you&#8217;ll be playing. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/rock-star/\" title=\"Rock Star\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">17. Rock Star</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/rock-star/\" title=\"Rock Star\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/rock-star.jpg\" alt=\"Rock Star\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233980\" sr