.</p>\n<p>It seamlessly integrates with almost every popular WordPress plugin. OpenEvent is easy to set up and highly optimized for performance.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-brooklyn/\" title=\"Brooklyn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">19. Brooklyn</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-brooklyn/\" title=\"Brooklyn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/brooklyn.jpg\" alt=\"Brooklyn\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233997\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/brooklyn.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/brooklyn-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/brooklyn-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-brooklyn/\" title=\"Brooklyn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Brooklyn</a> is a rocky WordPress music theme for bands, artists, musicians, and nightclubs. It comes with a large custom logo, navigation menu, musical slider, and support for SoundCloud. It also supports YouTube and Vimeo for video integration.</p>\n<p>It has multiple color styles, slideshow, social icons, and more. The theme is optimized for SEO and can be used to create a multilingual website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sessions/\" title=\"Sessions\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">20. Sessions</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sessions/\" title=\"Sessions\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sessions.jpg\" alt=\"Sessions\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233982\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sessions.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sessions-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sessions-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sessions/\" title=\"Sessions\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Sessions</a> is a beautiful WordPress theme for bands, musicians, and artists. Like other popular themes, It comes with an audio streaming player to play live music on your website. It has multiple custom post types to promote your content.</p>\n<p>It supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">drag and drop page builder</a> to design your custom layout. Sessions theme is compatible with WooCommerce to sell your event tickets online.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-dancefloor/\" title=\"Dance Floor\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">21. Dance Floor</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-dancefloor/\" title=\"Dance Floor\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/dancefloor.jpg\" alt=\"DanceFloor\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233998\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/dancefloor.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/dancefloor-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/dancefloor-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-dancefloor/\" title=\"Dance Floor\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Dance Floor</a> is a perfect WordPress DJ theme for musicians, dancers, nightclubs, and bands. It comes with an event calendar to display your upcoming events. You can also add this event calendar as a widget to the sidebar or footer of your website.</p>\n<p>This theme has multiple color styles, custom widgets, post types, and more. It also comes with a slideshow, audio track widget, and social media icons.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-berliner/\" title=\"Berliner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">22. Berliner</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-berliner/\" title=\"Berliner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/berliner.jpg\" alt=\"Berliner\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233990\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/berliner.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/berliner-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/berliner-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-berliner/\" title=\"Berliner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Berliner</a> is a modern WordPress music theme for bands, musicians, and DJs. It has a beautiful black and white layout with a full-width image, custom logo, navigation menu, upcoming events, and call-to-action button on the header.</p>\n<p>Other features include 6 content types, custom audio player, event management system, and flexible layout options. It&#8217;s optimized for SEO to help you <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">grow your traffic</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-nightclubbing/\" title=\"Nightclubbing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">23. NightClubbing</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-nightclubbing/\" title=\"Nightclubbing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/nightclubbing.jpg\" alt=\"Nightclubbing\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233991\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/nightclubbing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/nightclubbing-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/nightclubbing-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create a website</a> for your nightclub with amazing features, then <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-nightclubbing/\" title=\"Nightclubbing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Nightclubbing</a> is the right choice. It can also be used to build websites for musicians, DJs, bands, and artists. This theme has a bold and multi-color background to capture your users&#8217; eyeballs.</p>\n<p>It comes with custom color schemes, widgets, and header options. Nightclubbing supports video and audio streaming from third-party sources.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/euphony/\" title=\"Euphony\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">24. Euphony</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/euphony/\" title=\"Euphony\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/euphony.jpg\" alt=\"Euphony\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233992\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/euphony.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/euphony-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/euphony-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/euphony/\" title=\"Euphony\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Euphony</a> is a free WordPress theme for musicians and bands. It&#8217;s crafted beautifully with crisp typography, bright colors, and stylish icons. It also includes a fullscreen background with a custom logo, navigation menu, search bar, and audio player.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s bundled with featured content slider, sticky playlist, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/\" title=\"10 Best WordPress Testimonial Plugins to Add Social Proof\">testimonials</a>. Euphony theme can also be used to build your music blog.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-setlist/\" title=\"Setlist\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">25. Setlist</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-setlist/\" title=\"Setlist\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/setlist.jpg\" alt=\"Setlist\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233993\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/setlist.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/setlist-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/setlist-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-setlist/\" title=\"Setlist\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Setlist</a> is a WordPress music theme designed specifically for bands and artists. It features a photo carousel slider to display your posts, upcoming events, and music shows. It also integrates with YouTube and Vimeo videos beautifully in your articles and pages.</p>\n<p>It includes social media integration to share your music easily. This theme is easy to set up and supports drag and drop page builders to help you customize your website layout.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/musical-vibe/\" title=\"Musical Vibe\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">26. Musical Vibe</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/musical-vibe/\" title=\"Musical Vibe\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/musicalvibe.jpg\" alt=\"Musical Vibe\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233994\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/musicalvibe.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/musicalvibe-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/musicalvibe-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/musical-vibe/\" title=\"Musical Vibe\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Musical Vibe</a> is another free WordPress theme for bands, musicians, and musical instruments. It has a clean, simple, and beautiful layout with crisp typography. It allows you to add a phone number, email address, location, and social icons to the header.</p>\n<p>The theme features an <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Slider Plugins\">image slider</a> to showcase articles with a call-to-action button. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/showthemes-tyler/\" title=\"Tyler\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">27. Tyler</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/showthemes-tyler/\" title=\"Tyler\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tyler.jpg\" alt=\"Tyler\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233995\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tyler.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tyler-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tyler-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/showthemes-tyler/\" title=\"Tyler\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Tyler</a> is a stylish WordPress theme for events, musicians, and bands. This theme has excellent design and color options to increase your ticket sales. You can also showcase top musicians and performers on the homepage. It highlights your upcoming events prominently to help you build an audience.</p>\n<p>It offers space to display your upcoming events in the sidebar or articles. Tyler theme supports page builders to set up the website layout quickly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-oxium/\" title=\"Oxium\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">28. Oxium</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-oxium/\" title=\"Oxium\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oxium.jpg\" alt=\"Oxium\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233996\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oxium.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oxium-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oxium-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-oxium/\" title=\"Oxium\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Oxium</a> is a beautiful WordPress theme for musicians, bands, DJs, and event organizers. It has a sidebar navigation menu and content on the right side of the screen. It comes with an image slider, drag and drop homepage builder, and AudioIgniter plugin to embed music on your website.</p>\n<p>This theme includes custom widgets, theme options panel, and layout choices. It <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-themes-online-store/\" title=\"50+ Best WooCommerce Themes for Your Online Store\">supports WooCommerce</a> and is optimized for SEO.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress themes for bands and musicians. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-event-plugi