press/\">12 Best Instagram Plugins for WordPress in 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22594:\"<p>Looking for the best Instagram Plugins for WordPress?</p>\n<p>Instagram is an excellent marketing platform for bloggers and small businesses. With Instagram, you can share details about your business in a visually stunning manner and connect to your audience that can possibly be your next client.</p>\n<p>So why not use this platform to expand your reach and possibly generate more sales? The best way to do that is by linking your Instagram profile to your business website. That way you can reach out to a wider audience and increase the possibility of converting more leads.</p>\n<p>If you are wondering how to connect your Instagram profile to your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps\">business website</a>, we have got you covered. WordPress offers tons of plugins that let you do that effortlessly.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you some of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress that will let you display your Instagram feed right on your WordPress website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Envira Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Envira Gallery\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224643\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Envira Gallery </a>is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">WordPress gallery plugins</a> that helps you create visually striking photo and video galleries on your website. The plugin comes with a robust drag and drop builder that makes it possible to create a gallery within a few seconds. To make your gallery look more attractive, you can use the pre-built templates that the plugin offers.</p>\n<p>The plugin has been loaded with amazing built-in features. You can also extend its functionality with the help of addons. By activating these addons, you can integrate your website with any social platforms, including Pinterest and Instagram. Additionally, you can keep your albums organized, enable slideshows and full-screen lightbox mode, and do a lot more.</p>\n<p>With its WooCommerce addon, you can activate the eCommerce function too. Besides that, you can also protect your digital work by adding an extra layer of security which can either be a password, or a watermark.</p>\n<p>The plugin is fully responsive and is compatible with most of the popular plugins that you may be using on your website. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Instagram Feed By Smash Balloon</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon.png\" alt=\"Instagram Feed- Smash Balloon, Instagram plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"396\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234782\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon-300x153.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon-768x392.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Feed</a> is a thoroughly responsive, fully customizable and SEO-friendly Instagram feed plugin that is super easy to setup and use. You can use it to display multiple Instagram feed on your website and customize each of them individually. </p>\n<p>It lets you combine your photos and videos in a single feed. Alongside, you can share your Instagram stories too with your audience. Stories can be displayed on a popup lightbox, so you can keep your visitors engaged for a long time.</p>\n<p>The plugin offers 3 different layout styles to display your pictures. Just like on Instagram, you can highlight your important feeds to let people know about your special moments. You can also tweak your pictures with the built-in customization option to give them the perfect look. Without a doubt, this plugin has been one of the most loved Instagram feeds plugins on the market.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-theatre/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Instagram Theatre</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-theatre/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Theatre.png\" alt=\"Instagram Plugins, Instagram Theatre\" width=\"775\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234786\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Theatre.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Theatre-300x149.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Theatre-768x382.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-theatre/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Theatre</a> lets you display your Instagram pictures on your website in a visually impressive manner. The plugin comes with several layout options and offers 3 fully responsive templates as well. You also get to use the Tag Instagram Feed mode, using which you can specify a tag to search from the Instagram API.</p>\n<p>With the Location mode you can specify the location where your picture was taken. If you want, you can also specify multiple user ID so you can pull in pictures from different users. The plugin is fully responsive, meaning your pictures look good on a computer, mobile or a tablet.</p>\n<p>This plugin comes with several visual effects to keep your visitors entertained and engaged. From alternate layouts, delay intervals, to effect speed, this plugin has so much to offer. It is compatible with the latest versions of WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-feed-wpdancers/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Instagram Feed by WPDancers</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-feed-wpdancers/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers.jpg\" alt=\"Instagram Feed by WPDancers, \" width=\"775\" height=\"376\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234790\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers-300x146.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers-768x373.jpg 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers-330x160.jpg 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-feed-wpdancers/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Feed by WPDancers</a> is another brilliant plugin that you might want to check out. You can display your pictures in one of the 4 stylish layouts that the plugin offers &#8211; namely the Grid layout, Slide gallery, Polaroid layout, and the latest Map layout. The plugin also offers amazing real-time configurations. So you can select the transition style, the card skin, lightbox skin and a lot more.</p>\n<p>With the Moderate and Sleep options, you can control what to display on your site. You can use the toggle button to reject posts you do not want in your feed. The plugin also offers a range of beautiful skin options. That way you can select the one you like the best and integrate into your website for the best looks.</p>\n<p>The plugin also supports videos and allows you to add social share buttons. If you are not a fan of a very cluttered timeline, you can limit the number of posts that you want to display. The plugin exhibits super fast performance and is super flexible in terms of customization and design. Instagram Feed is overall easy to handle even if you&#8217;re using it for the first time. But if you still think that you need help, you can reach out to their friendly support team who is always ready to help you.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/modula-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >5. Modula</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/modula-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula.png\" alt=\"Modula Gallery plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234792\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula-300x118.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula-768x303.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/modula-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Modula</a> is a WordPress Gallery plugin that allows you to display your photographs beautifully on your site. You can integrate it with various social media platforms too, including Instagram. With Modula, you can display media from your Instagram feed. The plugin offers fantastic filter options that you can use to improve the way your images look.</p>\n<p>With its drag and drop builder, you can customize your galleries quickly and easily. You can use it to resize your images and build your own custom layout. The plugin is super responsive which makes the images look crisp and clear on the screen size of all types. </p>\n<p>Modula also lets your visitors browse through your galleries by filtering them based on dates, hashtags, etc. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. NextGen Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery.png\" alt=\"nextgen gallery\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217174\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">NextGen Gallery</a> is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">gallery plugins for WordPress</a>. by purchasing one single plugin you can actually gain access to functions of more than 30 different extensions together. The plugin offers 10 different layout styles to display your pictures and has options for image sharing, image linking, commenting, and even proofing your images from being stolen.</p>\n<p>Then there are tons of beautiful options for your images. You can add filters, pick your favorite theme, and use the image Lightroom options. Best of all, this plugin provides you with lifetime updates and free support. This plugin is a great option for anyone who is looking for a way to showcase their Instagram pictures stunningly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-widget/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Instagram Widget by Elfsight</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-widget/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight.jpg\" alt=\"Elfsight\" width=\"775\" height=\"516\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234799\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight-768x511.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-widget/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Widget</a> is yet another impressive plugin that lets you display your Instagram pictures on your website. You can use your hashtag or your username to add your pictures to your widget. The plugin is super flexible when it comes to customization. From adding colors, resizing your images to adding a scroll option, it comes with almost every Instagram integration feature you&#8217;ll need.</p>\n<p>It also responds very well to different gadgets and screen sizes. The plugin supports more than 16 different languages, so you can use this function to reach out and connect to more people. By adding the Follow button, you can encourage people to follow your site. This helps you attract more people and increase your fan base. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/feed-them-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Feed Them Social</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/feed-them-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social.png\" alt=\"Feed Them Social, Instagram Plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"362\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234803\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social-300x140.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social-768x359.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/feed-them-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Feed Them Social</a> is a free WordPress plugin that comes loaded with amazing Instagram integration features. You can add any kind of social feed to your WordPress website, and display it in the most stylish manner. The feed can either be Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest or any other social media. The plugin is super easy to install, setup and use.</p>\n<p>With Feed Them Social, you can display your pictures either on your posts, pages or sidebar. You can also generate a shortcode using its shortcode generator in a matter of seconds. The customization option is vasts too. You have full freedom to style your site the way you want.</p>\n<p>You can change the color and font, add a Like or Follow button above or below your feed, and do a lot more. The plugin receives regular updates and is compatible with the latest versions of WordPress. So do check it out now. More than 70k people are already using it on their website. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Soliloquy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review.png\" alt=\"Soliloquy\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224642\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Soliloquy</a> is an easy-to-use slider plugin for WordPress that lets you integrate your Instagram feed on your website sliders. With Soliloquy, you create featured content based on your posts, pages, and custom post types. It is also easy to create a lightbox slider to showcase your photos, videos, and galleries. </p>\n<p>You can even convert your PDFs and presentations to your sliders. The speed of the sliders can easily be controlled under the default settings. It is also possible that you schedule your sliders on your own timings. To protect your slider from being downloaded, you can disable the right click feature and ensure that your sliders are protected from theft or illegal use. </p>\n<p>The plugin is compatible with a lot of other advanced plugins too. The plugin is thoroughly responsive and looks stunning across platforms of all types.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Smart Slider 3</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider.png\" alt=\"Smart slider 3\" width=\"775\" height=\"369\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234808\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider-300x143.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider-768x366.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Smart Slider 3</a> is another slider plugin that offers the best way to add your Instagram feed in the form of sliders on your website. But the plugin does not limit itself to letting you create sliders alone. You can also create beautiful carousels and blocks as well.</p>\n<p>This plugin also has a free version, which you can download from WordPress.org. Although the free one is good to go, the pro version promises to take your sliders to another level. You have 2 skin options &#8211; light and dark. It also has tons of effects that can be added to your pictures for an enhanced look.</p>\n<p>With Smart Slider 3, you can add as many as 11 layers to your website. That itself offers an added glamour to your website. You also have animation effects to make your sliders look unique. The plugin also comes with a lot of customization options.</p>\n<p>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/enjoy-instagram-instagram-responsive-images-gallery-and-carousel/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. Enjoy Instagram</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/enjoy-instagram-instagram-responsive-images-gallery-and-carousel/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Enjoy-Instagram.png\" alt=\"Enjoy Instagram\" width=\"775\" height=\"377\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234811\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Enjoy-Instagram.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Enjoy-Instagram-300x146.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Enjoy-Instagram-768x374.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Enjoy-Instagram-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/enjoy-instagram-instagram-responsive-images-gallery-and-carousel/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Enjoy Instagram</a> is a free WordPress plugin that lets you integrate your Instagram feed with your WordPress website. It lets you use hashtags to display your Instagram photos. With the plugin, you can share your videos too. The number of rows and columns for your pictures are easily customizable.</p>\n<p>You can also use different effects to make your pictures look great. Make your pictures fade in for the Instagram Grid view, use lightboxes with image captions and navigation arrows, and more. The plugin is compatible with the latest versions of WordPress. </p>\n<p>Enjoy Instagram is well-optimized for mobile devices so you don&#8217;t have to bother about how it would look on smaller screens. The one-click setup option makes the plugin even more easy to use. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/instagram-widget-by-wpzoom/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">12. WPZoom Widget for Instagram</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/instagram-widget-by-wpzoom/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WPZoom.jpg\" alt=\"WPZoom Plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"617\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234813\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WPZoom.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WPZoom-300x239.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WPZoom-768x611.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/instagram-widget-by-wpzoom/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WPZoom Widget for Instagram</a> is another free Instagram widget plugin for WordPress that is super easy to use. The plugin is compatible with any WordPress theme and plugins. With this plugin, you can display a beautiful header with your bio and let people know the details of your feed.</p>\n<p>It also allows you to add the lazy load option, so you can only load images when they&#8217;re visible to your visitors. Because the plugin is fully customizable, you can have full control over how it appears to your visitors. You can use CSS to add some extra design and make it stand out from the rest of the websites.</p>\n<p>Overall this plugin is a great one. Besides, you get some really cool features to use without paying a single penny. The plugin receives regular updates and offers great support as well. So try it out now. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find some of the best WordPress Instagram plugins. Is there any other plugin that you have been using to display your Instagram feed on your website? If yes, do let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins for Engagement\">best social sharing plugins</a>.  </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-instagram-plugins-wordpress/\">12 Best Instagram Plugins for WordPress in 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-instagram-plugins-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0: