erinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension.png\" alt=\"Google Product Feed WooCommerce Extension\" width=\"620\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214310\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Google Product Feed plugin lets you create a real-time feed of your WooCommerce store’s products and services to the Google Merchant Center as a unique way of advertising. </p>\n<p>In fact, this extension automates the entire process of feeding product information to Google. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">20. MailChimp for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191104\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"MailChimp for WooCommerce plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"219\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce-300x106.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MailChimp is one of the most popular email marketing services available on the market. Their official WooCommerce plugin is <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">MailChimp for WooCommerce</a>.</p>\n<p>When installed on your WooCommerce website, the plugin automatically syncs your customers and their purchase data with your MailChimp account. Then, you can send targeted email campaigns to them and make more sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">21. WooMarketing Bundle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191118\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle.png\" alt=\"WooMarketing Bundle Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As its name suggests, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooMarketing Bundle</a> is a package of WooCommerce marketing extensions. It&#8217;s an official plugin from the WooCommerce team themselves.</p>\n<p>The bundle plugin includes email marketing, Facebook Ads integration, smarter discounts, transactional emails, social logins, etc.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an excellent offer if you want to implement all the marketing features included in it. Because buying separate plugins for each feature would cost you a lot more than purchasing this single plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-pack-and-ship-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">22. WooCommerce Pack &amp; Ship Bundle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-pack-and-ship-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191119\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Pack and Ship Bundle\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WooCommerce Pack &amp; Ship Bundle is a complete package plugin that enables you to sell, pack, and ship products worldwide. It&#8217;s also an official plugin from Team WooCommerce.</p>\n<p>The plugin comes with powerful features including responsive 360-degree image rotation, invoices, packing lists, product kits, multi-address shipping and tracking, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://hootsuite.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">23. Hootsuite</a></h3>\n<p>Utilizing the power of social media can expand your brand to a wider customer base and bring more traffic to your WooCommerce shop.</p>\n<p>However, running an online shop requires a lot of work. From administrative tasks to fulfilling orders, there&#8217;s not a lot of time to promote your company the way you want to.</p>\n<p>That’s where <a href=\"https://hootsuite.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hootsuite</a> comes in handy.</p>\n<p>In fact, Hootsuite helps with WooCommerce marketing automation by allowing you to schedule your social media posts in advance on up to 30 different social media platforms.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124458\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Marketing Tools - Hootsuite\" width=\"560\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite-300x206.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Not only does this save you time, but it also helps you gain more leads that can convert into sales.</p>\n<p>Not to mention you can communicate directly with your team in the Hootsuite dashboard, view detailed analytics reports, and use pre-written responses, automating your marketing process even more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">24. Product Import Export for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191121\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Product Import Export for WooCommerce\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Product Import Export for WooCommerce</a> allows you to import or export simple products in CSV format. If you need to send your product details to someone, the export feature comes in handy.</p>\n<p>Using this plugin, you can bulk upload and update products in your WooCommerce store. Hence, you don’t need to enter data for every single product manually.</p>\n<p>So, that’s it! The list of the 24 best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for maximizing your WooCommerce store revenue. We hope this article helped you to choose the plugins most useful for your website.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out our list of the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins for every website</a> (free + premium).</p>\n<p>Also, don’t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more WooCommerce guides and Google Analytics tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">24 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Your Traffic and Sales (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins: Which Is Best for You?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:129:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-wordpress-lms-plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"x