/groups/wpformsvip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-511542 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-vip-circle-announcement.jpg\" alt=\"vip circle announcement\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-vip-circle-announcement.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-vip-circle-announcement-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-vip-circle-announcement-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-vip-circle-announcement-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>Access Exclusive Benefits</h3>\n<p>The WPForms VIP Circle Group on Facebook grants you exclusive access to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>An active community full of WPForms power users</li>\n<li>Tips &amp; tricks to get the most out of WPForms</li>\n<li>Giveaways</li>\n<li>Tutorials</li>\n<li>Answers to questions for basic issues</li>\n<li>Sneak peeks at upcoming features</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You’ll find other business owners just like you, get ideas for new ways to use the plugin, and even have a chance to win prizes.</p>\n<p>So what are you waiting for?</p>\n<p>You can get started right now and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/wpformsvip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">click here to join the WPForms VIP Circle Group on Facebook</a>.</p>\n<p>We want to thank you for your continued support of WPForms. We look forward to continuing to help you grow your business and website.</p>\n<p><em>Lisa and the WPForms team</em></p>\n<p>Don’t have a WPForms Pro yet? <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/account\">Click here to upgrade today</a> and see why there are so many raving WPForms Pro fans.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/introducing-the-new-wpforms-vip-circle/\">Introducing the New WPForms VIP Circle</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://wpforms.com/introducing-the-new-wpforms-vip-circle/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"11 Best WordPress Plugins To Launch (+Grow) Your Podcast in 2019\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 22 Jul 2019 12:00:05 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"contact form\";s:7:\"attrib