"data\";s:27803:\"<p>Want to know which plugins are the best for launching and growing a successful podcast?</p>\n<p>There&#8217;s a ton of WordPress plugins out there, so this list narrows them down and shows you which ones are great to use if you&#8217;re about to start (or have been) podcasting.</p>\n<p>In this guide, we&#8217;ve listed the very best WordPress podcasting plugins to help you with your podcast.</p>\n<h3>Is WordPress Good for Podcasting?</h3>\n<p>WordPress is a fantastic choice for podcasting.</p>\n<p>While it&#8217;s true that you can host a podcast without a website, you&#8217;ll want to create a dedicated website for your podcast to reach its full potential and to <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/insanely-easy-ways-to-grow-your-email-list-fast-starting-now/\">grow your subscriber list</a>.</p>\n<p>Some of the top reasons WordPress is good for podcasting include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Allow your fans to access all episodes</li>\n<li>Give your audience a place to contact you through a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-simple-contact-form-in-wordpress/\">simple contact form</a> on a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-make-an-outstanding-contact-us-page-with-8-examples/\">contact us page</a></li>\n<li>Connect with listeners by sharing details about yourself</li>\n<li>Have somewhere for advertisers to learn more about your podcast</li>\n<li>Gain new listeners through search engine traffic</li>\n<li>Access podcast-specific layouts theme companies like <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Divi</a> offer (Helps you make a WordPress podcast theme)</li>\n<li>Expand your podcasting features with <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins-for-your-website/\">WordPress plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>However, you may be thinking that starting a website for your podcast is too much work. But it&#8217;s actually really easy if you use the right tools.</p>\n<h3>The Best WordPress Podcasting Plugins</h3>\n<p>Here are our top picks for the best WordPress podcasting plugins:</p>\n<h3>1. <a title=\"Blubrry\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/blubrry/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">PowerPress by blubrry</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Blubrry\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/blubrry/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516695\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blubrry-podcast-powerpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"blubrry podcast powerpress plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blubrry-podcast-powerpress-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blubrry-podcast-powerpress-plugin-300x118.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blubrry-podcast-powerpress-plugin-768x302.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blubrry-podcast-powerpress-plugin-1024x403.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easily the most powerful podcasting plugin on the market, <a title=\"Blubrry\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/blubrry/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">PowerPress</a> is an incredibly user-friendly tool to add podcasting to your WordPress site.</p>\n<p>And since it&#8217;s offered by Blubrry, you&#8217;ll also be able to get services like podcasting hosting and podcast statistics.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ability to import your Soundcloud podcast</li>\n<li>Easily set up a premium podcast with <a href=\"http://memberpress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MemberPress</a></li>\n<li>Add both audio and video podcasts to your site</li>\n<li>Supports Apple and Google podcasts and creates <a title=\"What is RSS? How to use RSS in WordPress?\" href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/what-is-rss-how-to-use-rss-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RSS feeds</a> for your podcast</li>\n<li>Fantastic organic growth through SEO</li>\n<li>Switch between simple and advanced mode to learn the plugin then use all its amazing features</li>\n<li>Integrated HTML5 media player with embed support for YouTube and more so you can embed your podcast into WordPress</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>PowerPress by blubrry pricing starts at $12/month for 100 MB.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/blubrry/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with PowerPress Today!</a></p>\n<h3>2. <a title=\"Smart Podcast Player\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smart-podcast-player/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Smart Podcast Player</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smart-podcast-player/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516698\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/smart-podcast-player-wordpress-plugin.png\" alt=\"smart podcast player wordpress plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/smart-podcast-player-wordpress-plugin.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/smart-podcast-player-wordpress-plugin-300x161.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/smart-podcast-player-wordpress-plugin-768x413.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/smart-podcast-player-wordpress-plugin-1024x551.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Smart Podcast Player\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smart-podcast-player/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Smart Podcast Player</a> is a great choice for power users who want to take their podcasting to a professional level. It&#8217;s one of the best WordPress podcasting plugins to help you set your podcast up on a website. It&#8217;s intelligent Smart Track Player is the biggest feature that sets this service apart from the others.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Beautifully-designed HTML player with share, download, and subscribe buttons</li>\n<li>Ability to promote your entire podcast archive</li>\n<li>The Smart Track Player is completely responsive and looks fantastic on desktops, tablets, and mobile devices</li>\n<li>Speed control features lets you add different playback speeds</li>\n<li>Customize your color theme to fit your podcast&#8217;s branding</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Smart Podcast Player pricing is $8.09/month (billed annually).</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smart-podcast-player/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with Smart Podcast Player Today!</a></p>\n<h3>3. <a title=\"BuzzSprout\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/buzzsprout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Buzzsprout</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"BuzzSprout\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/buzzsprout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516689\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/buzzsprout-podcasting.jpg\" alt=\"buzzsprout podcasting\" width=\"1116\" height=\"637\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/buzzsprout-podcasting.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/buzzsprout-podcasting-300x171.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/buzzsprout-podcasting-768x438.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/buzzsprout-podcasting-1024x584.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"BuzzSprout\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/buzzsprout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Buzzsprout</a> is a very popular and well-known podcast plugin that&#8217;s also a complete podcasting service. They offer podcasting promotion and podcast hosting as well.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple and easy-to-use user interface</li>\n<li>Automatic audio optimization as your file is uploading</li>\n<li>Ability to easily sync your episodes to popular podcast directories including Stitcher, iTunes, Google Play, and more</li>\n<li>Use podcast shortcodes from the free plugin to add your episodes to anywhere on your WordPress site</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Buzzsprout is free for up to 2 hours of audio/month, and starts at $12/month for 3 hours of audio/month.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/buzzsprout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with Buzzsprout Today!</a></p>\n<h3>4. <a title=\"SimplePodcastPress\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/simplepodcastpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Simple Podcast Press</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"SimplePodcastPress\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/simplepodcastpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516686\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/simple-podcast-press-podcast-hosting.jpg\" alt=\"simple podcast press podcast hosting\" width=\"1116\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/simple-podcast-press-podcast-hosting.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/simple-podcast-press-podcast-hosting-300x152.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/simple-podcast-press-podcast-hosting-768x390.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/simple-podcast-press-podcast-hosting-1024x520.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the simplest podcasting plugins for WordPress is appropriately named <a title=\"SimplePodcastPress\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/simplepodcastpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Simple Podcast Press</a>. It&#8217;s a podcast player and plugin specifically designed for hosting your episodes on WordPress so you can grow your audience with a website.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with all major podcasting platforms including Spreaker, BlogTalkRadio, PodBean, Soundcloud, and more</li>\n<li>Completely automatic so you can set it up then focus on producing more episodes</li>\n<li>Creates unique pages for each of your podcast episodes</li>\n<li>Customizable buttons</li>\n<li>Easy social sharing</li>\n<li>Automatic URL shortener</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Simple Podcast Press pricing starts at $67.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/simplepodcastpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with Simple Podcast Press Today!</a></p>\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/libsyn-podcasting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Libsyn Podcasting</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/libsyn-podcasting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516678\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/libsyn-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"libsyn wordpress plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/libsyn-wordpress-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/libsyn-wordpress-plugin-300x97.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/libsyn-wordpress-plugin-768x248.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/libsyn-wordpress-plugin-1024x331.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Using the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/libsyn-podcasting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Libsyn Podcasting plugin</a>, you can connect your WordPress website to your Libsyn account and start publishing podcasts easily. It&#8217;s a great option if you want to have your podcast on and off WordPress.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Since the episodes are stored on Libsyn, you won&#8217;t take up space on your <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WordPress hosting</a> and can access them if your site goes down</li>\n<li>Easily create podcast drafts and podcast episodes, then schedule them to post on your WordPress site</li>\n<li>Ability to use Apple Podcasts optimization tags</li>\n<li>Easy-to-user block editor</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Libsyn Podcasting pricing starts at $5/month for 50 MB.</p>\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/seriously-simple-podcasting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Seriously Simple Podcasting</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/seriously-simple-podcasting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516676\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/seriously-simple-podcasting-podcast-hosting.png\" alt=\"seriously simple podcasting podcast hosting\" width=\"1116\" height=\"373\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/seriously-simple-podcasting-podcast-hosting.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/seriously-simple-podcasting-podcast-hosting-300x100.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/seriously-simple-podcasting-podcast-hosting-768x257.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/seriously-simple-podcasting-podcast-hosting-1024x342.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the best podcasting plugins for WordPress for beginners to podcasting is <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/seriously-simple-podcasting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Seriously Simple Podcasting</a>. Because it&#8217;s free, it&#8217;s a good choice for a podcasting plugin for people just starting out.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Supports both audio and video podcasting</li>\n<li>Lets you run multiple podcasts on the same WordPress website</li>\n<li>Customizable media player to change colors and add your podcast image</li>\n<li>Supports most popular podcast platforms including iTunes, Stitcher, Google Play, and more</li>\n<li>Ability to use shortcodes and widgets to add your episodes, playlists, and archive anywhere on your WordPress site</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Seriously Simple Podcasting is free, but if you want unlimited storage, pricing starts at $19/month.</p>\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/podlove-podcasting-plugin-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Podlove Podcast Publisher</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/podlove-podcasting-plugin-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516664\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/podlove-podcast-publisher.png\" alt=\"podlove podcast publisher\" width=\"1116\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/podlove-podcast-publisher.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/podlove-podcast-publisher-300x101.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/podlove-podcast-publisher-768x259.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/podlove-podcast-publisher-1024x345.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/podlove-podcasting-plugin-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Podlove Podcast Publisher</a> is an open source podcasting plugin that&#8217;s free. It&#8217;s best for people looking for a customizable option with lots of features.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>An active online community</li>\n<li>Options for different templates</li>\n<li>Includes a HTML5 player to play your podcasts</li>\n<li>Supports multi-format publishing by using modern audio and video codecs</li>\n<li>Features chapter support to help you manage your podcast episodes easily</li>\n<li>Comes with analytics so you can see what your listeners are doing with your podcast</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Podlove Podcast Publishing is free, and if you&#8217;d like support, pricing starts at around $44/month.</p>\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-516655\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-best-podcasting-plugins-for-wordpress.png\" alt=\"wpforms best podcasting plugins for wordpress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-best-podcasting-plugins-for-wordpress.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-best-podcasting-plugins-for-wordpress-300x128.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-best-podcasting-plugins-for-wordpress-768x328.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-best-podcasting-plugins-for-wordpress-1024x437.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking to build a strong community of loyal podcast listeners, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">WPForms</a> is a must-have plugin for your podcasting website. Once you have your podcast listeners on your website, you&#8217;ll want the world&#8217;s best contact form builder plugin to help you keep them coming back.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy drag and drop builder to create tons of different types of helpful forms for your WordPress site</li>\n<li>Add contact forms in minutes to give your users and advertisers a way to reach you</li>\n<li>Create online order forms to accept payments via <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/stripe-addon/\">Stripe</a> and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/paypal-standard-addon/\">PayPal</a> to make money from your podcast</li>\n<li>A <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\">Survey and Polls addon</a> to uncover what your listeners want to hear more about in future episodes</li>\n<li>Gorgeous <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/conversational-forms-addon/\">conversational forms</a> to help capture the email addresses and information of your website visitors</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>WPForms Lite is free, and the feature-rich WPForms Pro is $199.50/year.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\">Click Here to Get Started with WPForms Today!</a></p>\n<h3>9. <a href=\"http://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-516658 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsights-pro-plugin-for-podcasts.jpg\" alt=\"monsterinsights pro plugin for podcasts\" width=\"1116\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsights-pro-plugin-for-podcasts.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsights-pro-plugin-for-podcasts-300x133.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsights-pro-plugin-for-podcasts-768x340.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsights-pro-plugin-for-podcasts-1024x453.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to know how people are finding your podcast website and what they do once they&#8217;re there, the <a href=\"http://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MonsterInsights</a> plugin is a must-have. It lands on this list of the best WordPress podcasting plugins since it makes it so easy to learn more about and grow your listener base.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/google-optimize/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Optimize tool</a> to let you conduct experiments with your content like A/B testing to find what works best for your site</li>\n<li>Get updated stats in real-time, so you can immediately see people going to your website as you mention it on your podcast</li>\n<li>A link tracking tool that helps you see which episodes are downloaded the most</li>\n<li>Ads tracking helps you see who is clicking on your Google AdSense ads so you can <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/effective-ways-to-sell-ad-space-on-your-wordpress-website/\">sell ad space on your WordPress website</a></li>\n<li>A user-friendly dashboard helps you see your podcast site&#8217;s performance right in your WordPress dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights Pro is $199.50/year.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with MonsterInsights Today!</a></p>\n<h3>10. <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509610 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster best wordpress podcasting plugins\" width=\"1116\" height=\"551\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates-300x148.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates-768x379.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates-1024x506.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re serious about capturing your podcast listeners attention and turning them into loyal fans and paying customers, <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is for you. It&#8217;s the most powerful lead generation software in the world and it&#8217;s a brilliant tool to use on any podcasting websites.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Monetize your podcast audience by turning your website traffic into leads, subscribers, and customers</li>\n<li>Mobile-friendly popups help you optimize your campaigns for tablets and mobile devices, where many podcast listeners visit your site from</li>\n<li>Create your own designs easily from scratch to match your podcast site&#8217;s branding</li>\n<li>Insanely effective <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Exit-Intent® Technology</a> detects a user&#8217;s mouse behavior and shows them a targeted message as they are leaving your site to help you <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/insanely-easy-ways-to-grow-your-email-list-fast-starting-now/\">grow your email list</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>OptinMonster Pro costs $29/month (billed annually).</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with OptinMonster Today!</a></p>\n<h3>11. <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RafflePress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-517123 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress.jpg\" alt=\"best wordpress podcasting plugins rafflepress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress-300x127.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress-768x326.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins-rafflepress-1024x434.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hands-down one of the easiest way to grow your podcast audience on your website is through <a href=\"http://rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RafflePress</a>. It&#8217;s a giveaway plugin that helps you coordinate your contests and giveaways from your podcast right on your WordPress site.</p>\n<p><b>Features:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Grow your podcast following and website traffic by sending listeners to your site to enter contests they hear about on your podcast</li>\n<li>Create beautiful, responsive online giveaways for your website in minutes</li>\n<li>Use pre-built giveaway templates to get more subscribers and improve engagement</li>\n<li>Integrates with your favorite <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-email-marketing-service-providers-with-free-options/\">email marketing services</a> so you can easily grow your email list</li>\n<li>Viral sharing feature helps automate word-of-mouth marketing to skyrocket your podcast&#8217;s growth</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>RafflePress pricing starts at $39 per year.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #659a17 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 20px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; line-height: 48px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://rafflepress.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click Here to Get Started with RafflePress Today!</a></p>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>And there you have it. We hope this post helped you find the best WordPress podcasting plugins to use and we wish you tons of success in your business online.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re just setting up your business, you should consider reading our <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-much-does-a-website-really-cost-beginners-guide/\">how much does a website really cost</a> post.</p>\n<p>And don&#8217;t forget to please follow us on <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> to get updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins/\">11 Best WordPress Plugins To Launch (+Grow) Your Podcast in 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-podcasting-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"Tableau Alternative: WPForms vs. Tableau (for Visualizing Survey Data)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://wpforms.com/tableau-alternative/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://wpforms.com/tableau-alternative/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 19 Jul 2019 12:00:47 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"small business forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"WPForms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"survey reporting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"survey form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=515658\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:572:\"<p>Looking for a more affordable and better way to visualize your survey data online? Using a Tableau alternative like WPForms can help you save tons of money and time. In this article, we&#8217;ll show you a WPForms vs. Tableau comparison to help you find the right Tableau alternative for you and your small business. What [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/tableau-alternative/\">Tableau Alternative: WPForms vs. Tableau (for Visualizing Survey Data)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9396:\"<p>Looking for a more affordable and better way to visualize your survey data online?</p>\n<p>Using a Tableau alternative like WPForms can help you save tons of money and time.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you a WPForms vs. Tableau comparison to help you find the right Tableau alternative for you and your small business.</p>\n<h3>What Is Tableau Used For?</h3>\n<p>Tableau is a powerful data analysis tool and popular BI (business intelligence) software. It&#8217;s used to connect to a data source, then simplify that information into a more understandable format. That way, people can make better business decisions using data analytics.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-515749\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-bi-software-dashboard.jpg\" alt=\"tableau bi software dashboard\" width=\"1116\" height=\"838\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-bi-software-dashboard.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-bi-software-dashboard-300x225.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-bi-software-dashboard-768x577.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-bi-software-dashboard-1024x769.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>The software is so robust and advanced, data analysts who want to make a career out of using Tableau can even get a Tableau Desktop Certification. Therefore, these data visualization professionals usually end up on business intelligence teams with highly-specialized jobs designing and creating Tableau dashboards.</p>\n<p>And Tableau is often used by huge companies with big budgets.</p>\n<h3>Can I Get Tableau for Free?</h3>\n<p>Asking yourself is Tableau worth the cost and looking to download Tableau free?</p>\n<p>So the answer is no, Tableau doesn&#8217;t offer Tableau Desktop for free. However, there are 2 exceptions to this:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>If you&#8217;re a full-time student, you can get Tableau Desktop <a href=\"https://www.tableau.com/academic/students\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">free for 1-year</a></li>\n<li>You can use a different platform called <a href=\"https://public.tableau.com/en-us/s/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Tableau Public for free</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Tableau does offer a free (not to be confused with open source) tool called Tableau Public. However, one of the biggest issues with Tableau Public is <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-security/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">security</a>.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re using Tableau Public, your business analytics are accessible by anyone on the internet.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-515764\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-public-data-visualizations-.jpg\" alt=\"tableau public data visualizations\" width=\"1116\" height=\"838\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-public-data-visualizations-.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-public-data-visualizations--300x225.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-public-data-visualizations--768x577.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tableau-public-data-visualizations--1024x769.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>This is because there&#8217;s no privacy to the files saved in the Tableau Public cloud, so anyone can download and access them at all times.</p>\n<p>But, this version is best for people who want to learn Tableau and just need a place to practice. As opposed to people who want to visualize survey data for their business.</p>\n<p>However, there&#8217;s a much safer, simpler, and affordable Tableau Alternative for visualizing your survey data— <a href=\"http://wpforms.com/pricing\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n<h3>WPForms vs. Tableau (for Visualizing Survey Data)</h3>\n<p>WPForms is a drag and drop WordPress plugin created specifically for small businesses and bloggers. And with the WPForms <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\">Surveys and Polls Addon</a>, even non-tech savvy people can quickly collect, view, edit, share, and analyze survey insights.</p>\n<p>Here are some reasons you may want to use WPForms vs. Tableau for your small business:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Extremely easy</strong> — Visualizing your survey data is accessible and easy for everyone</li>\n<li><strong>No advanced statistics degrees required</strong> — Small business users don&#8217;t always have the means to outsource data visualization and complex data interpretation just to understand their survey results</li>\n<li><strong>Built-in online reporting</strong> — You don&#8217;t have to leave your WordPress dashboard to see exactly what&#8217;s happening with your survey data in real-time</li>\n<li><strong>Easy survey creation</strong> — Not only can you use the survey tool to visualize your data, but you can build different kinds of surveys as well, including <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/beginners-guide-what-is-a-likert-scale-and-how-to-use-it/\">Likert Scales,</a> <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-net-promoter-score-nps-survey-in-wordpress/\">NPS Surveys</a>, polls, and basic surveys (Tableau is not a data creation tool)</li>\n<li><strong>No limited access</strong> — Any WordPress admin on your website can access your survey results, so you don&#8217;t have to pay for a license for each new user as your business grows</li>\n<li><strong>Affordable</strong> — The <a href=\"http://wpforms.com/pricing\">WPForms Pro plan</a> is available at around $200/year (around $17/month) with unlimited users while Tableau costs $70/month (nearly $840/year) for every single user, adding up to thousands of dollars if you need more than one user</li>\n<li><strong>Simple data integration</strong> — Access all your survey results on a single, easy-to-understand dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-504312\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/how-to-graphically-display-survey-data.gif\" alt=\"how to graphically display survey data\" width=\"1116\" height=\"610\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><p>Check out our post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/survey-question-best-practices-for-boosting-form-conversions/\">how to design a survey &#8211; best survey practices</a> for help boosting your conversions</p>\n</div>\n<h3>Visualization Data Tool + More</h3>\n<p>Many BI Solutions are super robust, including Tableau. You could end up overpaying for enterprise-level software with tons of advanced features. And you&#8217;ll never get to use them all because you don&#8217;t know how or simply don&#8217;t need them.</p>\n<p>And that&#8217;s another reason WPForms is the perfect small business Tableau alternative for survey data.</p>\n<p>WPForms is a great data visualization tool that automatically builds beautiful reports from your survey data. Take a look at this video to see the WPForms <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\">Surveys and Polls Addon</a> in action:</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/O69thfD5agY?rel=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe></p>\n<p>And on top of data visualization reporting tools, WPForms Pro has a bunch of other features to help you <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-power-hacks-to-grow-your-business-online/\">grow your business online</a> like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Powerful drag and drop form builder to create things like contact forms and surveys</li>\n<li>Smart conditional logic to display different survey fields based on user input</li>\n<li>Integrations with the most popular <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-email-marketing-service-providers-with-free-options/\">email marketing services</a></li>\n<li>Ability to accept payments via forms with the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/stripe-addon/\">Stripe</a> and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/paypal-standard-addon/\">PayPal</a> addons</li>\n<li>100&#8217;s of pre-built form templates to save you time building forms</li>\n<li>And more..</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>And that&#8217;s it for our WPForms vs. Tableau comparison. Hopefully, this post helped you find a good Tableau alternative for your small business.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;d like to see even more ideas for getting insight into your survey data, be sure to check out our post on the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/survey-data-visualization-tools/\">best survey data visualization tools.</a></p>\n<p>So what are you waiting for? Get started with the most powerful <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">WordPress forms plugin</a> today.</p>\n<p>And if you found this article helpful, please follow us on <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/easywpforms?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/tableau-alternative/\">Tableau Alternative: WPForms vs. Tableau (for Visualizing Survey Data)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10: