";s:8:\"blogging\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"wordpress.org\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"wordpress.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=514647\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:520:\"<p>Starting a blog and want to find the best blogging platform for beginners? It can be a tricky choice since it&#8217;s a big decision and there are a lot of unique options out there. In this post, we&#8217;ve made it easy for you to pick what works best for you with a list of the [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-blogging-platform/\">Which Is the Best Blogging Platform for Beginners? (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30439:\"<p>Starting a blog and want to find the best blogging platform for beginners?</p>\n<p>It can be a tricky choice since it&#8217;s a big decision and there are a lot of unique options out there.</p>\n<p>In this post, we&#8217;ve made it easy for you to pick what works best for you with a list of the best blogging platforms for beginners in 2019.</p>\n<p>So here are the top blogging platforms we’ll be comparing in this article. If you’re interested in a particular one, click the link in this list of blog sites to skip ahead in the post:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#wordpress.org\">WordPress.org</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#constantcontactbuilder\">Constant Contact Builder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gatorwebsitebuilder\">Gator Website Builder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#wordpress.com\">WordPress.com</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#squarespace\">Squarespace</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#blogger\">Blogger</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#weebly\">Weebly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tumblr\">Tumblr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#livejournal\">LiveJournal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#typepad\">Typepad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#medium\">Medium</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#ghost\">Ghost</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h3>How to Choose the Best Blogging Platform</h3>\n<p>Before diving into our list of the best blogging sites, it&#8217;s important to make sure you know what you’re looking for in a blogging platform.</p>\n<p>Ask yourself these 3 questions about blogging platforms:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Is it easy to set up?</strong> If you&#8217;re new to blogging or even just thinking about <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/start-a-wordpress-blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">starting a blog</a>, you may not be very technical yet (or may not ever be), so you want to look for a blogging platform that&#8217;s super user-friendly</li>\n<li><strong>Does it have the option for me to make money with my website?</strong> Even if it&#8217;s not something you want to do right now, you&#8217;ll want a platform that lets you make money off your site in case you want to do that in the future</li>\n<li><strong>Is it flexible so it can grow with my site?</strong> As your blog grows, you&#8217;ll want to change the look of your site and add new features to support your growing audience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So now that you have a better idea about exactly how to choose the best blogging platform, let&#8217;s take a look at our picks for the best blogging platforms for beginners for 2019.</p>\n<h3>Which Is the Best Blogging Platform for Beginners?</h3>\n<p>Here are the best blogging platforms for beginners:</p>\n<h3 id=\"wordpress.org\">1. <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WordPress.org</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-514654\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WordPress-content-management-system.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress content management system\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WordPress-content-management-system.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WordPress-content-management-system-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WordPress-content-management-system-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/WordPress-content-management-system-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Above all, the very best choice (and the most popular) for all bloggers is WordPress.org. It&#8217;s incredibly customizable and flexible, which explains why it powers over 30% of all the websites on the internet.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><p>Many blogging newbies confuse WordPress.org with WordPress.com. Check out our post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-pros-and-cons-compared\">WordPress.org vs WordPress.com</a> for a great comparison on WordPress blogging.</p>\n</div>\n<p>This is the best choice if you want full control over the future of your blog. <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WordPress.org</a> is a self-hosted WordPress option, meaning you&#8217;ll need a WordPress hosting provider. <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Bluehost</a> is by far the best solution to get started with WordPress.org.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Full and complete control over your blog</strong> — Using this robust Content Management System lets you create any kind of site from a blog to an <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-optimization-guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">eCommerce</a> store</li>\n<li><strong>Easily customize the look of your website</strong> — You can use themes like <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Divi</a>, <a title=\"Astra WordPress Theme\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Astra</a>, or <a title=\"OceanWP\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OceanWP</a> to make your site look exactly the way you want it</li>\n<li><strong>Amazing options for functionality</strong> — Your WordPress website can be enhanced in a ton of different ways by using <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins-for-your-website/\">plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Not always beginner-friendly</strong> — Can have a slight learning curve for non-technical people who don&#8217;t use helpful sites like <a href=\"http://wpbeginner.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPBeginner.com</a></li>\n<li><strong>Doesn&#8217;t handle security</strong> — You&#8217;ll need to manage your own backups and security (like with a plugin with <a title=\"Sucuri\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Sucuri</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free. You&#8217;ll need to pay to have a domain name for around $14.99 per year + hosting around $7.99 per month.</p>\n<p>Click <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">here</a> to get started setting up WordPress.org with Bluehost today.</p>\n<h3 id=\"constantcontactbuilder\">2. <a title=\"Constant Contact Website Builder\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact Website Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Constant Contact Website Builder\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-514694\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constant-contact-builder-best-blogging-platform-.jpg\" alt=\"constant contact builder best blogging platform\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constant-contact-builder-best-blogging-platform-.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constant-contact-builder-best-blogging-platform--300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constant-contact-builder-best-blogging-platform--768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constant-contact-builder-best-blogging-platform--1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re ready to a create a blog, <a title=\"Constant Contact Website Builder\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact&#8217;s Website Builder</a> is another fantastic choice to pick as your blogging platform since it&#8217;s so easy to use.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Freebies</strong> — A free domain and SSL certificate comes with all of their paid plans</li>\n<li><strong>Extensive free plan</strong> — Their great free plan comes with lots of features so you can start buil