art-a-blog-with-blogger-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/start-a-blog-with-blogger-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://blogger.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Blogger</a> is one of the oldest blog platforms around and requires a Google account to get started, but may have some major deal-breakers for some looking to grow their site.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Simple to start</strong> — Easily set up and create a blog without paying for anything</li>\n<li><strong>Backed by Google</strong> — The technology giant owns the platform so it&#8217;s secure and reliable</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dated</strong> — The platform doesn&#8217;t receive updates often</li>\n<li><strong>Design</strong> — The options for customization and design are extremely limited</li>\n<li><strong>Limited features</strong> — You can&#8217;t really grow your blog with the limited basic blogging tools that are provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free.</p>\n<h3 id=\"weebly\">7. <a href=\"http://weebly.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Weebly</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://weebly.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=no follow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514677 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/create-a-blog-with-weebly.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog with weebly\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/create-a-blog-with-weebly.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/create-a-blog-with-weebly-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/create-a-blog-with-weebly-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/create-a-blog-with-weebly-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weebly.com\" target=\"_blank\" re