y and isn&#8217;t a good fit for businesses or people trying to make money with a website.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>More options than just blogging</strong> — On top of writing blog posts, you can use social media tools, send and receive private messages, and join communities</li>\n<li><strong>Multi-language</strong> — Available in a ton of languages so you can <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-website-multilingual/\">make your website multilingual</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ads</strong> — Free sites have to show LiveJournal&#8217;s advertisements</li>\n<li><strong>Limited templates</strong> — No professional templates are available</li>\n<li><strong>Hobbyist level blogs</strong> — LiveJournal is not suitable for business or professional blogs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free.</p>\n<h3 id=\"typepad\">10. <a href=\"http://typepad.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Typepad</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://typepad.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=no follow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514686 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/typepad-for-blogging-sites.jpg\" alt=\"typepad for blogging sites\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/typepad-for-blogging-sites.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/typepad-for-blogging-sites-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/typepad-for-blogging-sites-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/typepad-for-blogging-sites-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://typepad.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Typepad</a> is a 100% blogging platform with lots of templates for design but limited options to add functionality to your site</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Tons of templates</strong> — 1,000&#8217;s of templates to pick from so you can change your blog&#8217;s design to whatever you would like it to look like</li>\n<li><strong>Analytics integration</strong> — Super easy to set up your blog and then connect it to Google Analytics to keep track of visitor behavior</li>\n<li><strong>Search engine</strong> — Built-in tools for searching</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hosted platform</strong> — Very limited customization options</li>\n<li><strong>Security </strong> — In April of 2014, the platform suffered from a <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/glossary/ddos/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DDoS</a> attack and has since dealt with a shadow of unreliability</li>\n<li><strong>Only a blogging platform</strong> — Since it&#8217;s 100% a blogging platform, you can&#8217;t add extra features like a eCommerce store</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Typepad pricing starts at $8.95.</p>\n<h3 id=\"medium\">11. <a href=\"https://Medium.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Medium</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://medium.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=no follow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514688 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/medium-and-the-best-blog-sites.jpg\" alt=\"medium and the best blog sites\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/medium-and-the-best-blog-sites.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/medium-and-the-best-blog-sites-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/medium-and-the-best-blog-sites-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/medium-and-the-best-blog-sites-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://medium.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Medium</a> is an online publishing platform that lets you import your content from anywhere on the web, but if you&#8217;re looking for the best blogging platform to make money, you&#8217;ll want to go with another one since you can&#8217;t monetize it.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ease of use</strong> — There&#8217;s barely any setup required</li>\n<li><strong>Reporting</strong> — Offers a powerful reporting tool so you can learn more about your readers and how they&#8217;re engaging with your posts</li>\n<li><strong>Focus on writing</strong> — It&#8217;s a content-first type of platform, so you can write and they handle the design</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>No monetization </strong>— You can&#8217;t make money off of the Medium platform</li>\n<li><strong>Content control</strong> — You have limited control over your content</li>\n<li><strong>Limited features</strong> — Very few options to customize your site</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Free.</p>\n<h3 id=\"ghost\">12. <a href=\"https://ghost.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Ghost</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ghost.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=no follow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514693 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/list-of-blog-sites-ghost-platform.jpg\" alt=\"list of blog sites ghost platform\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/list-of-blog-sites-ghost-platform.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/list-of-blog-sites-ghost-platform-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/list-of-blog-sites-ghost-platform-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/list-of-blog-sites-ghost-platform-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ghost.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Ghost</a> is a minimalist and open-source blogging platform that&#8217;s easy to use but lacks the ability to use many 3rd-party plugins.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Simple to use</strong> — A clean and modern interface keeps things easy for users</li>\n<li><strong>No setup</strong> — If you opt for the hosted version, setup is instant</li>\n<li><strong>Built-in SEO</strong> — The platform comes with SEO tools</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Limited customization</strong> — You can&#8217;t use most paid and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-themes/\">free themes</a> or plugins</li>\n<li><strong>Branded domain</strong> — Unless you buy a custom domain from a 3rd-party <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/how-to-choose-the-best-domain-registrar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">domain registrar</a>, your blog will be a Ghost subdomain ending with ghost.io</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost: </strong></p>\n<p>Self-hosting requires a custom domain around $14.99 per year + web hosting for around $7.99 per month.</p>\n<p>The hosted version starts at $29 per month for 2 users and up to 100,000 page views.</p>\n<h3>Final Thoughts</h3>\n<p>So which site is best for blogging?</p>\n<p>Out of all the most popular blogging platforms, we strongly recommend using <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WordPress.org</a> so you get complete control and flexibility over your blog and its future. <a title=\"Constant Contact Website Builder\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact Website Builder</a> and <a title=\"HostGator Builder\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/hostgator-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Gator Website Builder by HostGator</a> are also great choices for beginners looking for something easy to use.</p>\n<p>And that&#8217;s it! Hopefully, this list helped you decide which of the best blogging platforms is the right one for you and your blog.</p>\n<p>Since you&#8217;re at the beginning of your blogging journey, make sure to take a look at our article called <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-much-does-a-website-really-cost-beginners-guide/\">how much does a website really cost</a> so there are no surprises for what you&#8217;re in for!</p>\n<p>Don&#8217;t forget to please follow us on <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> to get updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-blogging-platform/\">Which Is the Best Blogging Platform for Beginners? (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://wpforms.com/best-blogging-platform/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"Which Is The Best Live Chat Software For Your Website? (Ranked)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://wpforms.com/best-live-chat-software/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://wpforms.com/best-live-chat-software/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 12:00:52 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"email marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"conversions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=512520\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:595:\"<p>Looking for the best live chat software for your website? Live chat software can explode your sales and increase customer satisfaction. In this guide, we&#8217;ve rounded up the best live chat software for WordPress sites. Why Is Live Chat Important? According to consumers, live chat is the preferred customer service method over email and phone. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-live-chat-software/\">Which Is The Best Live Chat Software For Your Website? (Ranked)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24223:\"<p>Looking for the best live chat software for your website?</p>\n<p>Live chat software can explode your sales and increase customer satisfaction. In this guide, we&#8217;ve rounded up the best live chat software for WordPress sites.</p>\n<h3>Why Is Live Chat Important?</h3>\n<p>According to consumers, live chat is the preferred customer service method over email and phone. When live chat is available on your website, reports of positive user experiences skyrocket. Here are the top reasons why consumers love live chat and why they think it&#8217;s so important for you to offer it on your website:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>To get questions answered immediately</li>\n<li>Ability to ask questions and multi-task</li>\n<li>It&#8217;s an efficient way to get customer support</li>\n<li>Consumers don&#8217;t like talking on the phone</li>\n<li>Better information than through emails/phone calls</li>\n<li>Can be done at work without disrupting coworkers by making a phone call</li>\n<li>They&#8217;re in control of the conversation</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So as you can see, consumers love and really want to ability to use live chat. And it&#8217;s important to note that live chat has a significant impact on online sales and marketing.</p>\n<p>So does live chat increase conversions? Absolutely.</p>\n<p>Most importantly, the best live chat software lets customers get instant answers from your brand without ever leaving your site. A positive live chat experience can easily help convince customers to make a purchase and so business with you again in the future.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Add Live Chat to My WordPress Site?</h3>\n<p>Asking yourself how do I set up live chat? It&#8217;s way simpler than you may think, especially with all the modern live chat software providers out there.</p>\n<p>A live chat tool is incredibly easy to add to your website. In most cases, you can add it to your website by using a live chat website plugin. For details on how that works, check out this great post on our sister site on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>So now that you know how easy it is to add live chat software to your WordPress site, let&#8217;s take a look at the best live chat software on the market.</p>\n<h3>Which Is The Best Live Chat Software For Your Website?</h3>\n<p>So, which is the best online chat? There&#8217;s a ton of them, so it&#8217;s easy to get overwhelmed with your choices. Here are our top picks, their features, and their cost:</p>\n<h3>1. <a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LiveChat</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512541\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/livechat-best-software-for-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"livechat best software for wordpress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"583\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/livechat-best-software-for-wordpress.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/livechat-best-software-for-wordpress-300x157.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/livechat-best-software-for-wordpress-768x401.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/livechat-best-software-for-wordpress-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/livechat-best-software-for-wordpress-625x328.jpg 625w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>When it comes to live chat software, <a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LiveChat</a> is hands-down the industry leader.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Beautifully designed live chat support apps</li>\n<li>Mobile-responsive so you and your agents can chat with customers on your laptops, tablets, and mobile devices</li>\n<li>Ability to add evaluation surveys before and after the live chat session</li>\n<li>Integrates with tons of other tools including email marketing services and other <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-marketing-automation-software/\">marketing automation software</a></li>\n<li>Lightning-fast loading time for a fantastic user experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>LiveChat pricing starts at $16 per month/per logged in agent (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They offer a 14-day free trial.</p>\n<p>Click <a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a> to get started with LiveChat now.</p>\n<h3>2. <a title=\"SendInBlue\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/sendinblue/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sendinblue</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"SendInBlue\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/sendinblue/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512543\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sendinblue-live-chat-for-your-website.jpg\" alt=\"sendinblue live chat for your website\" width=\"1116\" height=\"598\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sendinblue-live-chat-for-your-website.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sendinblue-live-chat-for-your-website-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sendinblue-live-chat-for-your-website-768x412.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sendinblue-live-chat-for-your-website-1024x549.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"SendInBlue\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/sendinblue/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sendinblue</a> is a powerful yet beginner-friendly live chat service that&#8217;s simple to install.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Built-in email marketing integration</li>\n<li>Retargeting for Facebook ads</li>\n<li>Complete <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-marketing-automation-software/\">marketing automation</a> with email marketing, <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/7-best-wordpress-crm-plugins-for-your-business/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CRM</a>, SMS, landing pages, and more</li>\n<li>Incredibly easy to use</li>\n<li>Workflow organization to keep your team on top of things</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>The Sendinblue chat feature pricing starts at around $44 per month/10 team members (billed annually).</p>\n<p>Click <a title=\"SendInBlue\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/sendinblue/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a> to start using Sendinblue today.</p>\n<h3>3. <a title=\"Olark\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/olark/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Olark</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Olark\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/olark/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512544\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/olark-online-chat-.jpg\" alt=\"olark online chat\" width=\"1116\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/olark-online-chat-.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/olark-online-chat--300x186.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/olark-online-chat--768x476.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/olark-online-chat--1024x634.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Olark\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/olark/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Olark</a> is another one of the best live chat solutions for websites and it&#8217;s also incredibly easy to use (and very popular).</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gives you a choice between a plugin or a simple code snippet install</li>\n<li>Integrates into Zendesk, <a title=\"HubSpot\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/hubspot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">HubSpot,</a> Salesforce, Google Analytics, Slack, and more</li>\n<li>Chat with customers from anywhere by using 3rd-party mobile apps to connect to mobile devices</li>\n<li>Proactive chats let you monitor live visitors on your site and reach out to them before they even touch the live chat window</li>\n<li>Real-time reporting on things like chat volume, which agents are handling the most chats, and how your website visitors are rating their experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Olark pricing starts at $15 per month/per agent (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They offer a 14-day free trial.</p>\n<h3>4. <a title=\"SnapEngage\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/snapengage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">SnapEngage</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"SnapEngage\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/snapengage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512545\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/snapengage-customer-service-website-chat.jpg\" alt=\"snapengage customer service website chat\" width=\"1116\" height=\"468\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/snapengage-customer-service-website-chat.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/snapengage-customer-service-website-chat-300x126.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/snapengage-customer-service-website-chat-768x322.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/snapengage-customer-service-website-chat-1024x429.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"SnapEngage\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/snapengage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">SnapEngage</a> is one of the pricier live chat solutions on our list but offers some unique features to justify that cost, so it might work perfect for you depending on your online business needs.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Call back requests</li>\n<li>Automated chat invitations</li>\n<li>Customizable chat widgets for professional-looking site branding</li>\n<li>SMS to Chat feature so agents can communicate via text</li>\n<li>Help your customers across multiple channels like Twitter, SMS, Facebook, WeChat, and more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>SnapEngage pricing starts at $16 per month/per user (minimum 3 users, billed annually).</p>\n<p>They also offer a 7-day free trial.</p>\n<h3>5. <a title=\"FreshChat\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/freshchat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Freshchat</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"FreshChat\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/freshchat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512546\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/freshchat-software-for-customer-support-chat.jpg\" alt=\"freshchat software for customer support chat\" width=\"1116\" height=\"584\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/freshchat-software-for-customer-support-chat.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/freshchat-software-for-customer-support-chat-300x157.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/freshchat-software-for-customer-support-chat-768x402.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/freshchat-software-for-customer-support-chat-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/freshchat-software-for-customer-support-chat-625x328.jpg 625w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Another fantastic and popular choice for the best live chat software for your website is <a title=\"FreshChat\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/freshchat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Freshchat</a>. It&#8217;s a modern tool designed to function as a conversion-boosting messenger and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/ultimate-guide-to-conversational-marketing/\">conversational marketing</a> app.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose between real-time chats with agents or AI-powered bots for automated conversations</li>\n<li>Customer timeline views to see the history of visitors with live profiles</li>\n<li>Lets your support team connect chats to tickets via Zendesk or Slack</li>\n<li>Offers desktop notifications so your team can stay alert and productive while responding to customers quickly</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Freshchat pricing starts at $15 per month/per agent (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They offer a limited free plan and a 30-day free trial.</p>\n<h3>6. <a title=\"Smartsupp\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smartsupp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Smartsupp</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Smartsupp\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smartsupp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512547\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-tool-and-chat-history.jpg\" alt=\"live chat tool and chat history\" width=\"1116\" height=\"555\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-tool-and-chat-history.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-tool-and-chat-history-300x149.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-tool-and-chat-history-768x382.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-tool-and-chat-history-1024x509.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Smartsupp\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/smartsupp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Smartsupp</a> is a simple and straightforward solution that may be best for those looking for an affordable live chat service.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Track and record user sessions to pin-point what&#8217;s stopping people from purchasing</li>\n<li>Works with WordPress, Shopify, Magento, OpenCart, Webnode, and more</li>\n<li>Customize the look of the chat to match your company colors</li>\n<li>Add personal photos of your agents to show customers there are real humans behind your business online</li>\n<li>The only live chat software offering video recordings of your site visitors</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Smartsupp pricing starts at $10 per month/per agent (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They offer a free plan for up to 3 agents, as well as a free trial.</p>\n<h3>7. <a title=\"Pure Chat\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/pure-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Pure Chat</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Pure Chat\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/pure-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512548\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/pure-chat-live-proactive-chat-solutions-.jpg\" alt=\"pure chat live proactive chat solutions\" width=\"1116\" height=\"668\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/pure-chat-live-proactive-chat-solutions-.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/pure-chat-live-proactive-chat-solutions--300x180.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/pure-chat-live-proactive-chat-solutions--768x460.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/pure-chat-live-proactive-chat-solutions--1024x613.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Pure Chat\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/pure-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Pure Chat</a> is another good alternative if you&#8217;re looking for limited features on a free plan, or a paid plan with lots of features so you can grow with your chat software as your business starts to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/make-money-online/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">make more money online</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Mobile apps so that you can stay connected with your customer on the go</li>\n<li>Customers have the option to send you email messages when your team is offline</li>\n<li>Pre-chat forms helps you collect user information (like issues or email addresses) before the conversation begins for a great user experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Pure Chat pricing starts at $79 per month (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They offer a robust free option as well with unlimited chat history.</p>\n<h3>8. <a title=\"Chaport\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/chaport/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Chaport</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Chaport\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/chaport/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-512549\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/chat-solutions-for-business-chaport.jpg\" alt=\"pure chat live proactive chat solutions\" width=\"1116\" height=\"597\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/chat-solutions-for-business-chaport.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/chat-solutions-for-business-chaport-300x160.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/chat-solutions-for-business-chaport-768x411.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/chat-solutions-for-business-chaport-1024x548.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Chaport\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/chaport/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Chaport</a> is easily the most affordable solution on this list of the best live chat software, so if saving money is your top priority, this one is definitely worth checking out.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Free version covers most basic requirements</li>\n<li>Live chat support apps for mobile devices</li>\n<li>Gorgeous multi-language chat widgets</li>\n<li>Analytics and reporting</li>\n<li>Integrations with tons of other services via Zapier</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Chaport pricing starts at $9.80 per month/per agent (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They offer a free version for up to 5 agents, and a 14-day trial for their paid plans.</p>\n<h3>9. <a href=\"https://www.zopim.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Zendesk Chat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zopim.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514078 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/zendesk-chat-customer-service.jpg\" alt=\"zendesk chat customer service\" width=\"1116\" height=\"572\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/zendesk-chat-customer-service.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/zendesk-chat-customer-service-300x154.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/zendesk-chat-customer-service-768x394.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/zendesk-chat-customer-service-1024x525.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zendesk is well known as a help desk support software, but they&#8217;ve recently acquired an existing live chat company to enter the live chat market with <a href=\"https://www.zopim.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Zendesk Chat</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integrated with industry leading support desk software (Zendesk)</li>\n<li>In-depth analytics</li>\n<li>AI-powered chatbots</li>\n<li>Stunning templates and customization options</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Zendesk Chat pricing starts at $14 per month/per agent (billed annually).</p>\n<p>They also offer a free trial of their highest tier plan (Enterprise).</p>\n<h3>10. <a href=\"https://www.liveperson.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LivePerson</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://liveperson.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"=nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514069 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-website-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"live chat website plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"571\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-website-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-website-plugin-300x153.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-website-plugin-768x393.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-website-plugin-1024x524.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.liveperson.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LivePerson</a> is possibly the most well-known live chat software out there since it&#8217;s been around for awhile and is quite established in the market. It&#8217;s a great pick for chat solutions for a business that&#8217;s operating on an enterprise level.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Robust and full of features</li>\n<li>Engage with customers via multiple channels including live chat, Messenger, WhatsApp, SMS, and more</li>\n<li>Create automated conversation flows</li>\n<li>Targeted toward medium to large business</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>LivePerson monthly pricing is negotiated on a case-by-case basis.</p>\n<h3>11. <a href=\"https://www.intercom.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Intercom</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://intercom.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514066 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-services-paid-plans.jpg\" alt=\"live chat services paid plans\" width=\"1116\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-services-paid-plans.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-services-paid-plans-300x151.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-services-paid-plans-768x385.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/live-chat-services-paid-plans-1024x514.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Intercom is a complete support software suite that includes live chat functionality. If you&#8217;re looking for a live chat software as well as a total support software (and can afford the price tag), <a href=\"http://intercom.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Intercom</a>&#8216;s many features are a good bet for your business.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Live chat widgets</li>\n<li>Automation for flows</li>\n<li>AI-powered Chatbots</li>\n<li>Many integrations with services like Slack, Google Analytics, and more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong></p>\n<p>Intercom&#8217;s pricing starts at $87 per month.</p>\n<p>They offer a 14-day free trial.</p>\n<h3>Best Live Chat Software: Winner</h3>\n<p>For small businesses, we recommend <a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LiveChat</a> and <a title=\"SendInBlue\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/sendinblue/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sendinblue</a>.</p>\n<p>Both are at the top of our best live chat software list since they are affordable, offer a fantastic user experience, and integrate with other software.</p>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>So there you have it. We hope this list of the best live chat software for WordPress helped you find the solution that works best for you and your business.</p>\n<p>With all the new customers you&#8217;ll have with your live chat software, you&#8217;ll need a way to reach out to them. Check out our guide on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-email-marketing-service-providers-with-free-options/\">the best email marketing services</a>.</p>\n<p>And if you like this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"https://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for more from our team.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-live-chat-software/\">Which Is The Best Live Chat Software For Your Website? (Ranked)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://wpforms.com/best-live-chat-software/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				