}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"small business forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"translation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"WPForms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=510748\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:586:\"<p>Do you want to add a translate button to your WordPress website? If you have website visitors who speak multiple languages, you definitely need to have a multi-language site. Luckily, it&#8217;s incredibly easy to do. In this post, we&#8217;ll show you how to make your WordPress website multilingual in just a few steps. What Is a [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-website-multilingual/\">How to Make Your WordPress Website Multilingual (The Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14620:\"<p>Do you want to add a translate button to your WordPress website?</p>\n<p>If you have website visitors who speak multiple languages, you definitely need to have a multi-language site. Luckily, it&#8217;s incredibly easy to do.</p>\n<p>In this post, we&#8217;ll show you how to make your WordPress website multilingual in just a few steps.</p>\n<h3>What Is a Multilingual Website?</h3>\n<p>A multilingual (or multi-language) website is a site that offers translated content in more than one language. For instance, English, Spanish, Ukrainian, and Chinese.</p>\n<p>The content and information (posts, site menu, etc) shown in different languages may be the same, but may also be customized for different audiences.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a multi-language website example from Polaroid&#8217;s site switching from English to French using <a title=\"Weglot\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/weglot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Weglot</a> for translations:</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-511415 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-plugin-translation-example.jpg\" alt=\"weglot plugin translation and WordPress Website Multilingual example\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-plugin-translation-example.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-plugin-translation-example-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-plugin-translation-example-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-plugin-translation-example-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Your small business website might not be on the scale of a huge camera and electronic business, but there are still a lot of different reasons why you might consider having a multilingual website which we&#8217;ll cover next.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><p>Looking to translate your WPForms plugin into another language besides the default language of English? WPForms is translation-ready for single language translations. Check out <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-translate-wpforms-into-a-different-language/\">how to translate WPForms into a different language</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<h3>Do I Need a Multilingual Website?</h3>\n<p>Asking yourself if you should offer multi-language on your site?</p>\n<p>Depending on where you are located and your target audience, you can choose to add translated versions of your site. Here&#8217;s some popular reasons people add multiple languages to their websites:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Boost Sales</strong> — You can increase your revenue when different audiences are able to use language switching, especially if it&#8217;s an <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-optimization-guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ecommerce site</a> with more than one common language</li>\n<li><strong>Better SEO</strong> — Lots of search engines are starting to run searches in foreign languages, so your traffic could increase with a multilingual site</li>\n<li><strong>Overcome Cultural Barriers</strong> — When you grant access to someone&#8217;s native language on your site, it shows you are cultural sensitive and lets the user feel more comfortable</li>\n<li><strong>Establish International Authority</strong> — If you&#8217;re looking to get ahead of competitors, showing that you&#8217;re a global brand can help</li>\n<li><strong>Gain Trust</strong> — Many people are much more likely to trust a website, a company, and its products when the content is displayed in their native language</li>\n<li><strong>Great User Experience</strong> — A multi-language website shows people you are thinking about your visitors and their experience on your site</li>\n<li><strong>Good ROI</strong> — Translation on your site is a cost effective marketing tool that can bring in new customers from all over the world&#8217;s population and help with <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/mobile-lead-generation/\">lead generation</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now, before you make your site multilingual, you need to make sure you have a WordPress.org website up and running. If you don&#8217;t have one yet, we recommend using <a title=\"Bluehost\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Bluehost</a> as your hosting provider. We did a comparison and Bluehost was the winner when we compared <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-hosting-guide/\">the best WordPress hosting</a>.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Make My WordPress Website Multilingual?</h3>\n<p>It&#8217;s easy to translate a WordPress site to multiple languages. Here&#8217;s how:</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install + Active the Weglot Plugin</h3>\n<p>First, sign up for a <a title=\"Weglot\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/weglot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Weglot</a> account and download the plugin. For help, check out this post on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Weglot&#8217;s multilingual tool lets you easily create a multilingual site (including forms) with minimal setup.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Configure the Settings</h3>\n<p>Once the plugin is activated, you&#8217;ll need to configure it&#8217;s settings. To do this, head over to your WordPress dashboard and click on Weglot to open the main configuration screen.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-510830 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"weglot multilingual wordpress website plugin \" width=\"1116\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-300x181.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-768x465.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-1024x619.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, log in to Weglot in another tab and find your API key. Come back to the other tab and paste your API Key into the API Key area in the settings page.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510838\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/add-api-key-weglot-multilingual-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"add api key weglot multilingual plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/add-api-key-weglot-multilingual-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/add-api-key-weglot-multilingual-plugin-300x181.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/add-api-key-weglot-multilingual-plugin-768x465.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/add-api-key-weglot-multilingual-plugin-1024x619.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, click on the dropdown menu and select the original language of your website. That way, Weglot knows which language to translate from.</p>\n<p>For this example, we&#8217;re using English since that&#8217;s the language the WPForm&#8217;s blog is written in.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510837\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/select-original-language-of-website.jpg\" alt=\"select original language of website\" width=\"1116\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/select-original-language-of-website.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/select-original-language-of-website-300x181.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/select-original-language-of-website-768x465.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/select-original-language-of-website-1024x619.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, add the destination language(s) you want your site to be translated into.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510844\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-select-destination-language.jpg\" alt=\"weglot multilingual plugin select destination language\" width=\"1116\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-select-destination-language.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-select-destination-language-300x181.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-select-destination-language-768x465.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/weglot-multilingual-plugin-select-destination-language-1024x619.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you can adjust different advanced settings including your flag icon, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/create-an-amp-friendly-contact-form-for-wordpress/\">AMP settings</a>, and exclusions.</p>\n<p>For now, let&#8217;s scroll down to the bottom of the settings page and click on the blue <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510879\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/save-change-weglot-plugin-setup-translation.jpg\" alt=\"save-change-weglot-plugin-setup-translation.\" width=\"1116\" height=\"661\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/save-change-weglot-plugin-setup-translation.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/save-change-weglot-plugin-setup-translation-300x178.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/save-change-weglot-plugin-setup-translation-768x455.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/save-change-weglot-plugin-setup-translation-1024x607.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Your site is now multilingual! Your website visitors can now see the flag icon right on the frontend of your WordPress website.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510897\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/default-language-flag-icon.jpg\" alt=\"default language flag icon\" width=\"1116\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/default-language-flag-icon.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/default-language-flag-icon-300x176.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/default-language-flag-icon-768x451.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/default-language-flag-icon-1024x602.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>If you click on the other flag icons, you can watch your site be automatically translated. This way, you can see how it will look for visitors. And you&#8217;ll know exactly what the user experience is like.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510899\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/language-switching-translated-content-example.jpg\" alt=\"language switching translated content example\" width=\"1116\" height=\"571\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/language-switching-translated-content-example.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/language-switching-translated-content-example-300x153.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/language-switching-translated-content-example-768x393.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/language-switching-translated-content-example-1024x524.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 3: Edit Your Translations</h3>\n<p>After you save your Weglot plugin&#8217;s settings on your site, you may want to edit your translations.</p>\n<p>Weglot automatically translate everything for you, but you can make your own tweaks.  To do so, click on the Edit my translations button in the top right of your Dashboard from the settings screen from the last step.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510881\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/edit-translations-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"edit translations plugin\" width=\"558\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/edit-translations-plugin.jpg 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/edit-translations-plugin-300x149.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>Clicking this will lead you to the translations page inside your Weglot account dashboard. You can also access that <a href=\"https://dashboard.weglot.com/translations/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-510885 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/how-to-edit-translation-in-weglot.jpg\" alt=\"how to edit translation in weglot with a wordoress multilingual website \" width=\"1116\" height=\"743\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/how-to-edit-translation-in-weglot.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/how-to-edit-translation-in-weglot-300x200.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/how-to-edit-translation-in-weglot-768x511.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/how-to-edit-translation-in-weglot-1024x682.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Weglot offers several different ways to add manual translations or to edit automatic translations. Check out <a href=\"https://support.weglot.com/article/128-how-to-edit-my-translations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">this helpful tutorial</a> for more details on their WordPress language switcher.</p>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>There you have it! You now know how to easily make your WordPress website multilingual with <a title=\"Weglot\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/weglot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Weglot</a>, the world&#8217;s best WordPress multilingual plugin.</p>\n<p>Now that you can translate your site into different languages, you should try using one of the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">best WordPress popup plugins</a> to turn all those new visitors into subscribers.</p>\n<p>If you like this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/easywpforms?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for more free WordPress tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-website-multilingual/\">How to Make Your WordPress Website Multilingual (The Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-website-multilingual/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"7 Best Business VoIP and Internet Phone Systems (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 12:00:20 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"small business\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"business VoIP services\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"internet phone systems\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"VoIP\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=510107\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:599:\"<p>Are you looking for the best VoIP system for your business? A VoIP or Voice over Internet Protocol is a cost-effective solution for small businesses. And unlike the traditional phone system, it comes with a number of useful features at no additional cost. In this article, we&#8217;ll compare the best business VoIP and internet phone [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/\">7 Best Business VoIP and Internet Phone Systems (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Sandipan Mukherjee\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14920:\"<p>Are you looking for the best VoIP system for your business? A VoIP or Voice over Internet Protocol is a cost-effective solution for small businesses. And unlike the traditional phone system, it comes with a number of useful features at no additional cost.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll compare the best business VoIP and internet phone systems and help you to decide the best one for your needs.</p>\n<h3>What Is VoIP? Why Is it Useful for Your Business?</h3>\n<p>A VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol) is a system that allows you to make or receive calls using the internet. It&#8217;s best suited for small businesses, entrepreneurs, and startups.</p>\n<p>It also offers additional features like caller ID, call forwarding, call management, voicemail, call waiting, and more. And you don&#8217;t need to pay anything for these features, unlike the traditional phone system.</p>\n<p>Some of the benefits of using a business VoIP system are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Make or receive calls using your computer, mobile (with the help of Android or iOS apps), and VoIP devices</li>\n<li>Ability to track and analyze the calls</li>\n<li>Cost-effective for small businesses and startups</li>\n<li>Share a single number with multiple employees</li>\n</ul>\n<p>With the above benefits in mind, let&#8217;s take a look at the best business VoIP and internet phone systems in 2019.</p>\n<h3>1. <a title=\"Nextiva\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Nextiva</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Nextiva\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510739\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/nextiva-business-voip-service.png\" alt=\"Nextiva business VoIP service\" width=\"1116\" height=\"604\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/nextiva-business-voip-service.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/nextiva-business-voip-service-300x162.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/nextiva-business-voip-service-768x416.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/nextiva-business-voip-service-1024x554.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Nextiva\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Nextiva</a> is one of the best and reliable VoIP services in the market. And you don&#8217;t need an annual contract to use their service.</p>\n<p>They offer some amazing features like unlimited calling, auto attendant, unlimited internet faxing, advanced call management, and more. You&#8217;ll also get a toll free number for free with all their plans.</p>\n<p>It comes with some automation features as well. For example, you can set up an action to occur at a specific time, or get automatic notifications when a new sale is made.</p>\n<p>The support team of Nextiva is extremely knowledgeable and helpful. You can always reach out to them in case you face any problem.</p>\n<p>Overall, Nextiva is suitable for startups, professionals, small businesses, and even mid-level businesses. We can also vouch for them as we use their VoIP service for some of our sister companies.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Starting from $20 per month for every single user.</p>\n<h3>2. <a title=\"RingCentral\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">RingCentral</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"RingCentral\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510741\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ringcentral.png\" alt=\"RingCentral Business VoIP service\" width=\"1116\" height=\"588\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ringcentral.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ringcentral-300x158.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ringcentral-768x405.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ringcentral-1024x540.png 1024w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ringcentral-625x328.png 625w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"RingCentral\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">RingCentral</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use VoIP service provider. Whether you&#8217;re planning to start your business or managing large businesses, you can use their reliable, secure, and hassle-free internet phone service.</p>\n<p>You can easily set up and activate their service within a few minutes. And you can always contact their team for help as they offer high-quality support to their customers.</p>\n<p>RingCentral comes with useful features including call monitoring, call forwarding, automatic call recording, video conferencing, and screen sharing.</p>\n<p>You can also integrate it with 3rd party apps and services like <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-simple-dropbox-upload-form-in-wordpress/\">Dropbox</a>, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-wordpress-google-drive-upload-form/\">Google Drive</a>, Zapier, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/the-easy-way-to-capture-leads-from-wordpress-to-salesforce/\">Salesforce</a>, Office 365, and more.</p>\n<p>Just like Nextiva, we can recommend you to use RingCentral for your business. The only concern is their pricing is on the higher side. However, you can use their annual plan to reduce your expenses.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Starting from $39.99 per user on a monthly basis. You can also pay annually and save up to 33%.</p>\n<h3>3. <a title=\"Phone.com\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Phone.com</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Phone.com\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510740\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/phone-com.png\" alt=\"Phone.com VoIP service\" width=\"1116\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/phone-com.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/phone-com-300x137.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/phone-com-768x350.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/phone-com-1024x466.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Phone.com\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Phone.com</a> is one of the most affordable VoIP services for small businesses. It offers different features like call forwarding, call waiting service, caller ID, voicemail, text messaging, and more.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll also get at least one local or toll-free number with all their plans. This is very useful for your business as customers can contact you at no cost to them.</p>\n<p>Do you want to learn about the demographics, social profile, etc of your customers? You can easily do that by taking a look at the caller analytics.</p>\n<p>Phone.com is a cost-effective service with their plans starting from $12.99 per month. However, there is a limit of 300 minutes and 3000 SMS with their basic plan. You need to upgrade to a higher plan to increase that limit.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Starting from $12.99 per month and comes with a 30-day money back guarantee.</p>\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://www.vonage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Vonage</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510749\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vonage-internet-phone-system.png\" alt=\"Vonage internet phone system\" width=\"1116\" height=\"496\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vonage-internet-phone-system.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vonage-internet-phone-system-300x133.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vonage-internet-phone-system-768x341.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vonage-internet-phone-system-1024x455.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Vonage is a plug and play VoIP service for small businesses. You just need a high-speed internet connection to start using their service.</p>\n<p>It offers unlimited calling and SMS service in the US and Canada. Plus, you can easily link your business phone number to your mobile with the help of their Android or iOS app.</p>\n<p>Vonage also comes with 40+ standard VoIP features including call screening, do not disturb, caller ID, call forwarding, voicemail to email, call blocking, and file sharing.</p>\n<p>However, you should note that their basic plan comes with limited features. So you need to upgrade to a higher plan to get all the premium features.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Starting from $19.99 per month, excluding taxes and other fees.</p>\n<h3>5. <a title=\"Grasshopper\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Grasshopper</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Grasshopper\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510755\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grasshopper.png\" alt=\"GrassHopper\" width=\"1116\" height=\"645\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grasshopper.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grasshopper-300x173.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grasshopper-768x444.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grasshopper-1024x592.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Grasshopper\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Grasshopper</a> is one of the best virtual phone systems in the market. And you can use their service if you&#8217;re an established small business owner or just starting out.</p>\n<p>It comes with the most essential features including incoming call control, call transfers, custom greeting, simultaneous call handling, VoIP calling, and voicemail with all their plans.</p>\n<p>To make outgoing calls, you can use their mobile or desktop apps. And there is no restriction on the number of minutes that you can use, unlike Phone.com.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Starting from $29 per month. It also offers a free trial to test their service.</p>\n<h3>6. <a href=\"http://www.voiceshot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Voiceshot</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510756\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/voiceshot.png\" alt=\"Voiceshot VoIP service\" width=\"1116\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/voiceshot.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/voiceshot-300x138.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/voiceshot-768x353.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/voiceshot-1024x471.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Voiceshot is a useful business VoIP service for startups. You don&#8217;t need any contracts to use their service.</p>\n<p>However, its basic plan comes with a limitation of 400 minutes per month, unlike Nextiva. And you&#8217;ll have to use a higher plan to increase that limit.</p>\n<p>Voiceshot offers a virtual auto attendant to answer the calls. It also comes with features like call forwarding, toll-free number, call transfer, caller ID, music on hold, scheduled greetings, and much more.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Starting from $12 per month.</p>\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://callhippo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">CallHippo</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-510754\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/callhippo.png\" alt=\"CallHippo\" width=\"1116\" height=\"554\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/callhippo.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/callhippo-300x149.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/callhippo-768x381.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/callhippo-1024x508.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>CallHippo is another great virtual phone system on our list. It comes with standard features like call hold, contact management, welcome message, call reminder, and more.</p>\n<p>It comes with a free plan with limited features and is suitable for entrepreneurs and startups. However, you can always upgrade to their higher plan to use the premium features.</p>\n<p>You can also integrate CallHippo to different services including <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-custom-pipedrive-wordpress-form/\">Pipedrive</a>, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-send-an-automatic-slack-invite-from-a-wordpress-form/\">Slack</a>, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-contact-in-zoho-from-a-wordpress-form/\">Zoho CRM</a>, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-contact-in-hubspot-from-a-wordpress-form/\">Hubspot</a>, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-install-and-use-zapier-addon-with-wpforms/\">Zapier</a>, and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-custom-support-ticket-form-on-wordpress-with-zendesk/\">Zendesk</a> to enhance its functionality.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Basic plan is free for up to 2 users.</p>\n<h3>Which is the Best VoIP and Internet Phone System for You?</h3>\n<p>After comparing the above services, we can conclude that <a title=\"Nextiva\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Nextiva</a> is the best VoIP service for small businesses and startups. They offer amazing features that are useful for most businesses.</p>\n<p>Also, you don&#8217;t need any annual contracts for using their service.</p>\n<p><a title=\"RingCentral\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">RingCentral</a> is another internet phone system that we can highly recommend. However, Nextiva has a slight edge over RingCentral, thanks to its cheaper pricing plans.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you choose the best business VoIP and internet phone system.</p>\n<p>If you are wondering how you can create a free professional email address for your business, then you may want to check out our step by step guide on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-setup-a-free-business-email-address/\">how to set up a free business email address in 5 minutes</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, please follow us on <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> to get updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/\">7 Best Business VoIP and Internet Phone Systems (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"[2019] 8 Best WordPress Popup Plugins to EXPLODE Your Email List\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 10 Jul 2019 12:00:48 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"OptinMonster\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"popup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"email marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=508939\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:595:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress popup plugins to turn your site visitors into subscribers and paying customers? Popup plugins are a wildly popular and effective way to get more subscribers and sales on your website. In this article, we&#8217;ve listed the very best WordPress popup plugins to skyrocket your email list in 2019. Best WordPress [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">[2019] 8 Best WordPress Popup Plugins to EXPLODE Your Email List</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26746:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress popup plugins to turn your site visitors into subscribers and paying customers?</p>\n<p>Popup plugins are a wildly popular and effective way to get more subscribers and sales on your website.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ve listed the very best WordPress popup plugins to skyrocket your email list in 2019.</p>\n<h3>Best WordPress Popup Plugins</h3>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a summary of our list of the best WordPress popup plugins:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#optinmonster\">OptinMonster</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#trustpulse\">TrustPulse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#icegram\">Icegram</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#ninjapopups\">Ninja Popups</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#bloom\">Bloom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#thriveleads\">Thrive Leads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sumo\">Sumo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#popupmaker\">Popup Maker</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Do I Need a WordPress Popup Plugin?</h3>\n<p>Asking yourself how do I create a custom popup in WordPress? You&#8217;ll need a WordPress popup plugin to do it.</p>\n<p>However, most <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">email marketing</a> services do let you create a simple popup form.</p>\n<p>But the biggest con to using a generic and simple popup form on your site is that they can be unattractive and fail to grab your visitor&#8217;s attention.</p>\n<p>So if you really want to boost the growth of your email list, you’ll need to create visually appealing popup forms that are targeted to your unique visitors. A simple and the most popular way to do this is by using popups with a plugin.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-509920\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/whats-the-best-wordpress-popup-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"whats the best wordpress popup plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/whats-the-best-wordpress-popup-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/whats-the-best-wordpress-popup-plugin-300x161.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/whats-the-best-wordpress-popup-plugin-768x413.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/whats-the-best-wordpress-popup-plugin-1024x551.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>But there are a lot out there, so how do you choose the best WordPress popup plugin?</p>\n<h3>How to Choose the Best WordPress Popup Plugin?</h3>\n<p>When choosing the best WordPress popup plugin, we suggest you look for a solution that:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Offers a wide-range of popup templates</li>\n<li>Is easy to use</li>\n<li>Has different campaign types</li>\n<li>Provides customizable triggers for popups</li>\n<li>Integrates with your email marketing service</li>\n<li>Has excellent customer support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Popups can <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/insanely-easy-ways-to-grow-your-email-list-fast-starting-now/\">grow your email list</a> like crazy, especially when used correctly as an email opt form. But popups can sometimes irritate your visitors, therefore ruining the user experience on your site.</p>\n<p>To avoid this, be very selective about the WordPress popup plugin you pick. It&#8217;s important to make sure you go with one that has lots of features, looks professional, and lets you control when it&#8217;s activated.</p>\n<p>Worried about setting up your popup plugin? Don&#8217;t be. Next, let&#8217;s take a look at how easy the best WordPress popup plugins are to set up.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Use Popup Plugins in WordPress?</h3>\n<p>To use popup plugins in WordPress, you simply need to install and activate the software. For help, check out this great article on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Every popup plugin on this list ended up here because it&#8217;s relatively easy to set up and has lots of helpful docs to get you up and running.</p>\n<p>With that said, let’s take a look at our picks for the best popup plugins for WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Which Is the Best WordPress Popup Plugin?</h3>\n<p>Let&#8217;s go ahead and take a peek at the pros and cons of each product so you can find the best WordPress popup plugin for you.</p>\n<h3 id=\"optinmonster\">1. <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509610 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster popup templates\" width=\"1116\" height=\"551\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates-300x148.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates-768x379.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/optinmonster-popup-templates-1024x506.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OptinMonster</a> is a powerful online lead generation software that&#8217;s used by millions of websites. It&#8217;s signature <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Exit-Intent® technology</a> helps convert abandoning visitors into subscribers and paying customers. It&#8217;s simply the best popup plugin on the market.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Exit-Intent®</strong> — Convert visitors leaving your website into leads by displaying a targeted campaign when they’re about to abandon your site.</li>\n<li><strong>Advanced Targeting</strong> — OptinMonster has not only page level targeting but advanced display rules like referrer detection, geolocation, and more.</li>\n<li><strong>Easy to use</strong> — Features a drag and drop builder for simple setup and customization.</li>\n<li><strong>Popup Templates</strong> — Choose from pre-built popups or start from scratch and build one.</li>\n<li><strong>Campaigns</strong> — Create popup campaigns for lightbox popups, floating bars, countdown timers, content lockers, fullscreen welcome mats, and slide-in scroll boxes.</li>\n<li><strong>Use on multiple sites</strong> —  OptinMonster is a SaaS (software as a service), so you can use one account on multiple websites.</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong> — Access fantastic customer service with their knowledgeable support staff.</li>\n<li><strong>Spin to win</strong> — Use a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-discount-wheel-popup-plugins/\">discount wheel popup</a> to maximize your conversions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>No free option</strong> — OptinMonster has no free version. But if you&#8217;re serious about <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/make-money-online/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">making money online</a>, it&#8217;s well worth the cost for those advanced features.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does OptinMonster Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>OptinMonster pricing ranges from <strong>$9 &#8211; $49 per month</strong> (billed annually).</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Get started with OptinMonster today</a>!</p>\n<h3 id=\"trustpulse\">2. <a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TrustPulse</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://trustpulse.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509618 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/trustpulse-wordpress-website.jpg\" alt=\"trustpulse wordpress website\" width=\"1116\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/trustpulse-wordpress-website.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/trustpulse-wordpress-website-300x137.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/trustpulse-wordpress-website-768x350.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/trustpulse-wordpress-website-1024x466.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Social proof popup notifications are a new and popular way to grow your email list (and boost your sales).  And because <a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TrustPulse</a> is the most powerful social proof app for business sites, we definitely had to include it on this list of the best WordPress popup plugins. It helps increase trust, conversions, and sales by displaying sleek-looking social proof notifications on your website.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Uses urgency</strong> — Works as a FOMO (fear of missing out) plugin by creating a feeling of urgency with timely notifications</li>\n<li><strong>Supports multiple platforms</strong> — Use it on all popular website platforms, including WordPress, Squarespace, Drupal, Shopify, and others</li>\n<li><strong>Tracking</strong> — Track purchases, downloads, and registrations on your site, then show them as recent activity</li>\n<li><strong>Customizable</strong> — Choose exactly where and when to display notifications to convert more users into customers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Limited sessions</strong> — The free version is capped at 500 sessions per month, but it&#8217;s affordable to increase that limit and get access the advanced features</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does TrustPulse Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>TrustPulse pricing ranges from <strong>free to $350+ per month</strong> (billed annually).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Get started with TrustPulse today</a>!</p>\n<h3 id=\"icegram\">3. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Icegram</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509621 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram-plugins-for-wordpress.png\" alt=\"icegram plugins for wordpress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram-plugins-for-wordpress.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram-plugins-for-wordpress-300x116.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram-plugins-for-wordpress-768x298.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram-plugins-for-wordpress-1024x397.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the newer options on this list is <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Icegram</a>, a service that helps you create popups and email optins to grow your email list. Besides creating popups and optin forms, you can make engaging Call To Action (CTA) buttons to drive visitors to any page you want (including affiliate links).</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cost</strong> — Icegram is a freemium plugin that is free to use, but premium addons with advanced features cost money</li>\n<li><strong>No traffic limit</strong> — Unlike some of the others on this list, there&#8217;s no traffic limit, so you can keep using it even if your site gets tons of visits</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Poor user interface </strong>— The user interface is hard to use and not intuitive. It doesn’t have a drag and drop builder, so creating even a simple popup form can be hard</li>\n<li><strong>Limited targeting </strong>— There&#8217;s only basic targeting such as time-based targeting, so this solution lacks a ton of options that could help you get more conversions</li>\n<li><strong>Unattractive built-in templates </strong>— It&#8217;s a free solution, so the templates don&#8217;t look great and could turn visitors away if they think your site looks unprofessional</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does Icegram Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>Icegram is a freemium software, meaning it&#8217;s <strong>free</strong> but premium addons range from $7 &#8211; $27.</p>\n<h3 id=\"ninjapopups\">4. <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/ninja-popups-for-wordpress/3476479\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Ninja Popups</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/ninja-popups-for-wordpress/3476479\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509628 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-create-popups.jpg\" alt=\"ninja forms create popups\" width=\"1116\" height=\"793\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-create-popups.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-create-popups-300x213.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-create-popups-768x546.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-create-popups-1024x728.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/ninja-popups-for-wordpress/3476479\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Ninja Popups</a> is a popular and straightforward popup plugin for WordPress sites and has lots of email marketing integrations. It helps you build simple popup forms in a visual drag and drop interface.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Active developer </strong>— Ninja popups is updated frequently to address any bug issues and new features</li>\n<li><strong>User interface</strong> — Use a drag and drop builder to build forms visually</li>\n<li><strong>Animation</strong> — Access dozens of effects to optimize your popups</li>\n<li><strong>Analytics</strong> — Use their built-in A/B testing</li>\n<li><strong>Mobile ready</strong> — Popups look good on phones and tablets</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Very basic targeting</strong> &#8211; Their targeting rules are extremely basic. They don&#8217;t have geo-targeting, UTM targeting, or other advanced targeting rules like OptinMonster has.</li>\n<li><strong>Limited campaign options</strong> &#8211; Ninja Popups is focused just on popups, so they don&#8217;t offer floating bars or other campaign types to maximize your conversions.</li>\n<li>Limited form customization &#8211; Ninja Popups doesn&#8217;t allow you to create your own custom HTML forms, so make sure they integrate with your service provider.</li>\n<li><strong>No free version</strong> — You have to pay to use this product at all</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does Ninja Popups Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>Ninja Popups pricing starts at <strong>$26.</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"bloom\">5. <a title=\"Bloom\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Bloom</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Bloom\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509631 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bloom-popup-maker-and-optin-form.jpg\" alt=\"bloom popup maker and optin form\" width=\"1116\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bloom-popup-maker-and-optin-form.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bloom-popup-maker-and-optin-form-300x120.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bloom-popup-maker-and-optin-form-768x308.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bloom-popup-maker-and-optin-form-1024x410.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Built by and offered to customers of Elegant Themes, <a title=\"Bloom\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Bloom</a> is a WordPress popup builder plugin that can save you some money if you&#8217;re already using one of their <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-small-business/\">themes for your small business</a>. It lets you build beautiful popup forms right from your WordPress dashboard. Bloom also offers a great demo site to test it out.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Built-in templates —</strong> Pick from 100&#8217;s of templates, so you don’t have to build a form from scratch</li>\n<li><strong>Dashboard </strong> — Access a custom panel in the WordPress dashboard with detailed reports on conversion rates and more</li>\n<li><strong>A/B testing </strong>— Compare the performance of one popup to another with split testing in Bloom and figure out which one is the most effective</li>\n<li><strong>Bundled with a theme</strong> — Can be cost-effective if you were planning to use a theme like Divi from Elegant themes</li>\n<li><strong>Campaigns </strong>— Pick from 6 different display types like optin popup, optin fly-ins, and others</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Speed </strong>— Using Bloom on WordPress sites could slow them down and impact performance and user experience</li>\n<li><strong>No visual customizer </strong>— You’ll need to click on the preview button to view any changes you make to your form.</li>\n<li><strong>Lacks features </strong>— While it offers most essential tools, it still lacks many useful features that OptinMonster offers like an exit-intent trigger.</li>\n<li><strong>Targeting </strong>— Bloom only offers basic targeting options</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does the Bloom Plugin Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>Bloom is priced at <strong>$89 a year or $249 for lifetime access</strong>, and includes access to the site builder <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Divi</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"thriveleads\">6. <a title=\"Thrive Themes\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/thrive-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Thrive Leads</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Thrive Themes\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/thrive-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509633 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/thrive-leads-email-opt-popup-form.jpg\" alt=\"thrive leads email opt popup form Best WordPress Popup Plugins\" width=\"1116\" height=\"631\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/thrive-leads-email-opt-popup-form.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/thrive-leads-email-opt-popup-form-300x170.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/thrive-leads-email-opt-popup-form-768x434.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/thrive-leads-email-opt-popup-form-1024x579.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Just like Bloom, Thrive Leads also lets you create gorgeous popup and optin forms right from your WordPress dashboard. <a title=\"Thrive Themes\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/thrive-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Thrive Leads</a> is another list building plugin by a theme company (Thrive Themes), and they&#8217;re specialized in creating conversion focused WordPress themes and plugins.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pay just once </strong>— The one-time payment for Thrive Leads lets you download the plugin and use without a recurring payment</li>\n<li><strong>Advanced analytics </strong>— Get detailed insights into your list building efforts and conversion rates with data reports and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/form-analytics/\">form analytics</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Speed </strong>— Thrive Leads is a huge plugin that could negatively impact your site&#8217;s performance</li>\n<li><strong>Ease of use</strong> — Getting started with Thrive Leads can be pretty difficult, even for experienced WordPress users</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does Thrive Leads Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>Thrive Leads pricing ranges from <strong>$67 &#8211; $147</strong>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"sumo\">7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sumome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sumo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sumome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509637 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-sites-and-conversion-rates.jpg\" alt=\"wordpress sites and conversion rates\" width=\"1116\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-sites-and-conversion-rates.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-sites-and-conversion-rates-300x120.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-sites-and-conversion-rates-768x306.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-sites-and-conversion-rates-1024x408.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Aside from being one of the best WordPress popup plugins, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sumome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sumo</a> also helps you with social sharing and analytics with things like heat maps and a scroll box. Just like OptinMonster, SumoMe is also a standalone solution.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Free </strong>— It doesn&#8217;t cost anything to use the limited features, but the free version shows blue notification bars across your site, which screams unprofessional to some visitors</li>\n<li><strong>Create popups based on traffic source </strong>— Create customized popups for people based on how your visitor got to your site (premium version)</li>\n<li><strong>Pre-built templates </strong>— Choose from a list of pre-designed templates specific to your popup goals (premium version)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Limited features </strong>— Lacks a lot of specialized features and targeting options for popups since it&#8217;s a broad product with other focus areas</li>\n<li><strong>Traffic limit </strong>— You&#8217;ll pay more if you get a lot of traffic with Sumo&#8217;s pricing model</li>\n<li><strong>Expensive </strong>— Best features are in the premium version, so if you’re looking for just a simple popup plugin, Sumo might not be a good fit for you</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does Sumo Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>Sumo pricing ranges from <strong>free to $39 per month</strong> (billed annually).</p>\n<h3 id=\"popupmaker\">8. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Popup Maker</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-509645 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/premium-version-email-opt.jpg\" alt=\"premium version email opt\" width=\"1116\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/premium-version-email-opt.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/premium-version-email-opt-300x83.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/premium-version-email-opt-768x212.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/premium-version-email-opt-1024x283.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Popup Maker</a> is another popular free WordPress popup plugin. It has multiple optin popup types and campaigns like lightbox popups, slide-in popups, sticky popups, notification popups, and more. You&#8217;ll also have the option to customize the look and location of your optin popup.</p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Free </strong>— Use this plugin at no cost</li>\n<li><strong>Features</strong> — Even the free version has a lot of tools for you to use</li>\n<li><strong>Triggers </strong>— Add click-based triggers to your navigation menu, buttons, sidebars, images, sidebars, and more</li>\n<li><strong>Form builder integration </strong>— Easily integrate your popups with popular contact form plugins like <a title=\"WPForms\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">WPForms</a></li>\n<li><strong>Targeting options </strong>— Set up conditional targeting and control where to show your popup like any other powerful popup maker</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Exit intent </strong>— The exit intent feature is not free (or robust) and is only available if you pay for it, so you could lose a lot of conversions without that advanced feature</li>\n<li><strong>Popup analytics </strong>— You won&#8217;t see popup analytics to track your campaigns in the free version of Popup Maker</li>\n<li><strong>Advanced targeting </strong>—You’ll have to purchase an addon to access helpful features like advanced targeting conditions, and the price could add up to the cost of a premium plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How Much Does Popup Maker Cost?</strong></p>\n<p>Popup Maker pricing ranges from <strong>free to $16 per month</strong> (billed annually).</p>\n<h3>Final Thoughts</h3>\n<p>If you&#8217;re still wondering which is the best popup plugin for WordPress, our vote is <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n<p>For the amount of features you get at the price, it&#8217;s the best choice by a mile. And since your email list is such an important part of your business online, you owe it to yourself to go with a premium WordPress popup plugin.</p>\n<p>And there you have it. We hope this list of the best WordPress popup plugins helped you find the solution that fits your needs so you can grow your email list and boost your online sales.</p>\n<p>Looking for more helpful tools for your site? Check out our post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins-for-your-website/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">the best WordPress plugins</a> to find all kinds of cool features.</p>\n<p>And if you like this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"https://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a> for more from our team.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">[2019] 8 Best WordPress Popup Plugins to EXPLODE Your Email List</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:25:\"https://wpforms.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:9:{s:6:\"server\";s:13:\"nginx/1.15.10\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Fri, 26 Jul 2019 08:16:32 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:10:\"set-cookie\";s:98:\"srv_id=64fd515db0370e752ab9384b7787d180; expires=Fri, 26-Jul-19 09:16:32 GMT; max-age=3600; path=/\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Thu, 25 Jul 2019 19:55:01 GMT\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"e61bdaa5d5c91a0f57515df07a4ae5c2\"\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:9:\"x-backend\";s:22:\"awesomemotive-web5.com\";s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";s:13:\"max-age=86400\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20190718142551\";}', 'no');
